NK015(ba)026:0: sgyu 'phrul zhi ba'i bsgom khog lam rim gsal ba'i sgron me'i dbu phyogs so //
NK015(ba)026:2: gu ru d+he wa d+h+aa ki la na mo /
NK015(ba)026:3: bla ma dang lhag pa'i lha la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK015(ba)026:4: sgyu 'phrul zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa'i rim pa 'di lag tu blangs pa'i lugs la /
NK015(ba)026:5: spyi don gyi khog phub pa dang /
NK015(ba)026:6: gzhung don nyams su len pa gnyis so //
NK015(ba)026:8: chos dang chu gnyis phug nas bshad par bya ba yin pas /
NK015(ba)026:9: chos rgyud dri ma med pa 'di'i lugs la /
NK015(ba)026:10: dang po sangs rgyas kyis gsungs /
NK015(ba)026:12: rgya gar mkhas grub rnams kyis bkral /
NK015(ba)026:13: lo pan skyes mchog rnams kyis bsgyur /
NK015(ba)026:14: rje btsun gong ma rnams kyi gsung tshig dri ma med pas brgyan no //
NK015(ba)026:16: thugs sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba la le'u stong phrag brgya pa yod pa za hor gyi yul na bzhugs /
NK015(ba)026:18: sgyu 'phrul sde brgyad bshad rgyud sde bzhi /
NK015(ba)026:19: khyad par du rtsa rgyud gsang ba'i snying po le'u
NK015(ba)026:20: nyi shu rtsa gnyis pa 'di zhi khro gnyis kyi
NK015(ba)026:21: rgyud yin te / le'u bcu bzhi pa yan chad ma bsgyur rnal ma'i dkyil 'khor /
NK015(ba)026:22: bco lnga pa man chad bsgyur ba khrag 'thung gis dkyil 'khor ston pa yin no //
NK015(ba)026:23: sdud pa po'i sdud lugs ni /
NK015(ba)026:24: gsang bdag phyag na rdo rje'i thugs kyi rnam 'phrul yin no //
NK015(ba)026:25: rgya gar mkhas grub rnams kyis bkral lugs ni /
NK015(ba)026:26: 'di la pan chen du ma'i thugs dam byas kyang /
NK015(ba)026:27: khyad par du sgyu 'phrul la mkhas pa sangs rgyas gsang bas /
NK015(ba)026:28: zhi ba la sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba /
NK015(ba)026:29: khro bo la snang ba dam pa rgyan zhes pa'i gzhung byas nas yod /
NK015(ba)026:30: lo pan skyes mchog rnams kyis bsgyur lugs ni /
NK015(ba)026:33: 'dir re zhig pan+ti ta b+hi ma la mi tra'i zhal nas /
NK015(ba)026:34: lo tsha ba rin chen mchog gis bsgyur bar 'dod mod kyang /
NK015(ba)026:35: dam pa bde bar gshegs pas ni /
NK015(ba)026:37: rje btsun gong mi'i gsung gis brgyan lugs la /
NK015(ba)026:38: stod kyi grub chen so zur gnub gsum gyi phyag len logs su shes la /
NK015(ba)026:39: 'di ni dam pa bde bar gshegs pas mdzad pa'i chog bsgrigs yin no /
NK015(ba)026:45: slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang ba //
NK015(ba)026:46: phyogs bcing brgyad kyi rim rdzogs nas //
NK015(ba)026:48: mchod rdzas byin gyis brlabs par bya //
NK015(ba)026:49: bdud rtsi chus bsang bgegs bskrad 'dug /
NK015(ba)026:51: bla ma bshes gnyen nas bzung ste /
NK015(ba)026:52: ye shes sku mchog gi bar tshang bar bya'o //
NK015(ba)026:53: khyad par du 'di nyid kyis sngon 'gro ni /
NK015(ba)026:54: kun rdzob dang don dam pa'i sems ye shes su bskyed pa gnyis las /
NK015(ba)026:55: dang po kun rdzob sems bskyed ni /
NK015(ba)026:56: badga dang mtha'a yasa pa'i semsa can rnams /
NK015(ba)026:57: ye gdoda ma nasa sangsa rgyas yin mod kyang /
NK015(ba)026:58: ma rtogsa pa'i dbang gisa 'khora ba la 'khyamsa pa rnams /
NK015(ba)026:59: byang chub mchog sangs rgyas thob pa'i ched du zhi
NK015(ba)026:60: ba rdo rje sems dpa'i dkyil 'khor bsgom par sems
NK015(ba)026:61: bskyed do // don dam sems bskyed ni /
NK015(ba)026:63: snang ba bzhis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad skye ba med pa la ngam zhing ngo matshara zhes pas /
NK015(ba)026:64: thams cad skyes pa la dam rmad kyis chosa zhes pa /
NK015(ba)026:65: skyes pa nyid na skye ba med pa la mtshar ba'o //
NK015(ba)026:66: de dag tshogs gnyis yang dag rdzogsa pa'i sangsa rgyas
NK015(ba)026:67: sku lnga po kun gyis thugs kyi brnag bya yin
NK015(ba)026:69: don dam pa byang chub kyi sems la snang ba
NK015(ba)026:70: bzhis skye ba meda pa lasa kun rdzob byang chub
NK015(ba)026:71: kyi sems la thamsa cad skye ba'o //
NK015(ba)026:72: de ltar kun rdzob kyi bden pa la skyes pa'i
NK015(ba)026:73: dus nyid na'ang don dam pa'i bden pa la skye
NK015(ba)026:74: ba meda pa'i phyir bden gnyis dbyer med du la
NK015(ba)026:75: bzla ba'o // de ni sems lnga las g.yo ldang byang chub kyi sems /
NK015(ba)026:77: ye shes lnga las stong pa nyid kyis ye shes so //
NK015(ba)026:78: de'i 'gres kyi 'og ma bzhi po la yang shes par bya ste /
NK015(ba)026:79: e ma rdzogsa pa'i chos nyid 'agga pa med pa
NK015(ba)026:80: lasa kun rdzob tu thamsa cada 'agga par ltar snang
NK015(ba)026:81: / kun rdzob tu 'agga pa'i dus de nyid na'ang
NK015(ba)026:82: chos nyid la 'agga pa meda pa'i phyir bden gnyis
NK015(ba)026:83: dbyer med du la bzla ba'o //
NK015(ba)026:84: de ni 'jig 'jug byang chub kyis sems so //
NK015(ba)026:85: mngon par byang chub pa'i sku /
NK015(ba)026:86: me long lta bu'i ye shes so //
NK015(ba)026:87: e ma rdzogas pa'i chos nyid la gansa para bya ba dang gnas par byed med pa la /
NK015(ba)026:88: kun rdzob tu thamsa cada gnas pa ltar snang /
NK015(ba)026:89: kun rdzob tu gnas pa'i dus de nyid na'ang chos
NK015(ba)026:90: nyid la gansa pa med pa'i phyir dbyer med du
NK015(ba)026:91: la bzla ba'o // gnas pa byang chub kyi sems /
NK015(ba)026:94: e ma rdzogsa pa'i chos nyid la dmigas para bya
NK015(ba)026:95: ba'i yul meda pa lasa kun rdzob tu thamsa cad
NK015(ba)026:97: kun rdzob tu dmigas pa'i dus de nyid na'ang chos
NK015(ba)026:98: nyid la dmigas pa meda pa'i phyir dbyer med du
NK015(ba)026:99: la bzla ba'o // de ni smon pa byang chub kyi sems /
NK015(ba)026:101: so sor rtogs pa'i ye shes so //
NK015(ba)026:102: e ma rdzogsa pa'i chos nyid la phyir 'gro ba
NK015(ba)026:103: dang nang du 'onga ba meda pa yin pa lasa
NK015(ba)026:104: kun rdzob tu thams cad 'gro ba dang 'ong ba
NK015(ba)026:105: ltar snang / kun rdzob tu 'gro ba dang 'ong
NK015(ba)026:106: ba'i dus de nyid na'ang chos nyid la 'gro 'ong
NK015(ba)026:107: meda pa'i phyir bden gnyis dbyer med du la bzla
NK015(ba)026:108: ltar snang / ba'o // de ni mthar phyin pa byang chub kyi sems /
NK015(ba)026:110: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes so //
NK015(ba)026:111: gong gi sems bskyed de ni lta ba'i ngo bo yin te /
NK015(ba)026:112: gsang sngags ma h+aa yo ga'i lugs kyi ma skyes
NK015(ba)026:113: mi 'gags dbyer med spros dang bral ba don dam
NK015(ba)026:114: pa lhag pa'i chos sku chen po yin pas /
NK015(ba)026:115: skye ba med pa ni don dam bden pa /
NK015(ba)026:116: 'gag pa med pa ni kun rdzob bden pa /
NK015(ba)026:117: gnas pa med pa ni dbyer med bden pa /
NK015(ba)026:119: 'gro 'ong med pa gnyis ni spros dang bral ba'i bden pa yin par shes par bya'o //
NK015(ba)026:120: lta ba de nyid nyams su len par byed pa la /
NK015(ba)026:121: blo rab 'bring tha ma gsum yod de /
NK015(ba)026:122: blo rab kyis bskyed rdzogs ro mnyam zung 'jug nyams su len pa yin te /
NK015(ba)026:123: slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang bas /
NK015(ba)026:124: sgom pa rnam bzhi zung ldan par //
NK015(ba)026:125: gdod ma nyid nas goms par byed //
NK015(ba)026:128: rim gnyis mnyam par bzhag nas ni /
NK015(ba)026:129: rdo rje can gyi chos 'chad do //
NK015(ba)026:131: rgya gar gyi na ro pan chen yang 'di'i rjes su 'brang ba yin no //
NK015(ba)026:132: blo 'bring gis don dam lam du khyer nas kun rdzob gtan la phab pa yin te /
NK015(ba)026:134: don dam kun gyi rgyu yin phyir //
NK015(ba)026:135: lhag pa'i don de dang por bsgom //
NK015(ba)026:139: rgya mtsho 'jing gi pha wang ltar //
NK015(ba)026:140: bskal par lam la btsal byas kyang //
NK015(ba)026:141: don med snying po skem pa yin //
NK015(ba)026:144: bskyed rim kun rdzob la brten nas don dam gtan la phab pa yin te /
NK015(ba)026:145: dmigs pa dag la brten nas su //
NK015(ba)026:146: mi dmigs pa dag rab tu skye //
NK015(ba)026:149: bskyed pa'i rim la legs gnas shing //
NK015(ba)026:150: rdzogs pa'i rim pa 'dod rnams la //
NK015(ba)026:151: thabs 'di rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyis //
NK015(ba)026:152: rim gnyis mnyam par bzhag pa'o //
NK015(ba)026:155: don dam skye med kyi gnas lugs gdangs 'gag pa
NK015(ba)026:156: med par lha'i dkyil 'khor du shar lugs bshad pa'o
NK015(ba)026:157: // spyi don gnyis pa dngos gzhi la /
NK015(ba)026:158: ting nge 'dzin gsum gyi khog phub pa dang /
NK015(ba)026:159: cho 'phrul bzhi'i gzhung bsrang ba gnyis so //
NK015(ba)026:161: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK015(ba)026:162: 'di ltar dngosa por snang ba rnams ni snang dus
NK015(ba)026:163: nyid na dngosa po med para rang snang bas na
NK015(ba)026:164: yul du rtog pa'i ngag gis smra ba dang blos
NK015(ba)026:165: bsam pa'i yul lasa 'adsa pa'i chos nyid ma bcos
NK015(ba)026:167: 'da' nyams med pas na ting nge 'dzin zhes bya'o //
NK015(ba)026:169: khams gsum gyi semsa can rnams la snying brtse ba'i phyir snying rje bsgom ste /
NK015(ba)026:170: dper na nam mkha' la ni nam mkha' bzhag pa
NK015(ba)026:171: bzhin du chos nyid de bzhin nyid las ma g.yos
NK015(ba)026:172: par 'gag med du snying rje kun snang gis ting
NK015(ba)026:173: nge 'dzin bsgom pas kun du snang ba'i ting nge
NK015(ba)026:174: 'dzin zhes bya'o // gsum pa rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK015(ba)026:176: rten gzhal yas khang lha dang bcas pa bskyed pa'i
NK015(ba)026:177: rgyu yin pas na rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin zhes bya'o
NK015(ba)026:178: // de yang skye med mtshon pa'i yi ge a
NK015(ba)026:179: ni yi ge thams cad kyi phyi mo'am mchoga yin
NK015(ba)026:180: // pas / de ni bskyed rim pas snying ka'i thad du bsgoma para bya ste /
NK015(ba)026:181: de yang byang chub kyi sems dri ma med pa mtshon pa'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)026:182: a dakara po ste rab tu gsal zhing brtan par gyur nas a dkar po de las /
NK015(ba)026:183: shin tu phra ba'i a rnams spro ste /
NK015(ba)026:184: a s+pha ra ra na phata /
NK015(ba)026:185: a dkar po de la brten nasa de la a dkar po gciga spros /
NK015(ba)026:186: de la brten nas gnyis spros /
NK015(ba)026:187: de la brten nas bzhi spros te /
NK015(ba)026:188: de bzhina du je manga je manga je ringa je ring du spro ba ni /
NK015(ba)026:189: dang po dbugs kyis sleb tshad tsam /
NK015(ba)026:190: de nas dris tshor tshad tsam /
NK015(ba)026:191: de nas mig gis mthong tshad tsam /
NK015(ba)026:192: de nas nam mkha'i khyab par spros te /
NK015(ba)026:193: gcig rjes su gcig gzhugas nas semas kyis khyab tshad a dakara po yungsa 'bru tsam gyis ganga nasa /
NK015(ba)026:195: slara 'oda zera tshur bsdus kyang gzhi po'i a ma 'phela /
NK015(ba)026:196: phyir la manga po spros kyang gzhi po'i a ma 'grib /
NK015(ba)026:197: de byang chub semsa kyi mtshan nyid yin para shes para bya'o //
NK015(ba)026:199: gsal brtan gyi tshad brgyad dang ldan pa dgos te /
NK015(ba)026:208: cir yang bsgyur du btub pa ste brgyad de /
NK015(ba)026:209: gnyis pa cho 'phrul bzhi'i gzhung bsrang ba la gnyis la /
NK015(ba)026:210: dang po rten bskyed pa ni /
NK015(ba)026:211: bris bsgom 'chad gsum gyi dbang du bshad dgos te /
NK015(ba)026:212: bris pa sa nas sa ru ste //
NK015(ba)026:213: bsgom pa sa nas gnam du gzhal /
NK015(ba)026:215: / 'chad pa don rtags sbyar te bshad //
NK015(ba)026:218: 'gying phur gyis shul du tshon lnga rim pa ltar blug nas bkang ba ni /
NK015(ba)026:219: 'byung ba rim brtsegs bri ba'i dbang du'o //
NK015(ba)026:221: a lasa e yam bam lam sum ram rnamas spros pa las /
NK015(ba)026:222: e lasa chos 'byung gru gsum mthing nag rgya khyon nam mkha'a dang manyama pa /
NK015(ba)026:223: des steng du yam las rlung zhes gzhung bzhin no //
NK015(ba)026:224: de'ang 'chad pa don rtags sbyar te bshad na /
NK015(ba)026:227: gsang ba ltar ye shes lnga dang sbyar bar bya'o //
NK015(ba)026:228: yang na phyi ltar 'byung ba lnga /
NK015(ba)026:230: gsang ba ltar yum lnga'i mkha' klong lngar 'dod par snang ba 'thad par mthong ngo /
NK015(ba)026:232: / 'byung ba rim brtsegs ri rab dang bcas pa bsgom tshar nas /
NK015(ba)026:233: rdo rje'i gur khang kha bskang ba ni /
NK015(ba)026:234: a lasa h'u mthinga naga gciga spros te 'od du zhu ba lasa /
NK015(ba)026:235: rdo rje rgya gram shar gyi rwa dakara /
NK015(ba)026:239: lte ba mthing nag h'u gis mtshan para gyur /
NK015(ba)026:240: de 'od du zhu ba las rdo rje'i gur khang du gyur te /
NK015(ba)026:241: 'og gzhi rdo rje'i brag ris gtam pa /
NK015(ba)026:242: phyi nang thams cad me ri 'bar bar bsgom /
NK015(ba)026:244: rdo rje'i rwa bas bdud dpung 'joms /
NK015(ba)026:245: me ri 'bar bas nyon mongs bsreg pa'i rtags so //
NK015(ba)026:246: a lasa b+h+r+aum spros pa lasa /
NK015(ba)026:248: chos kyi dbyingsa kyi rang bzhina zhes gzhung bzhin no //
NK015(ba)026:249: b+h+r+aum cir yang 'gyur ba'i sa bon yin te /
NK015(ba)026:250: skabs 'dir gzhal yas khang bskyed pa'i sa bon du 'gyur la /
NK015(ba)026:252: bi shud+d+he ni rnam par dag pa ste /
NK015(ba)026:253: 'byung ba lngar 'dzin gyi rtog pa dag nas /
NK015(ba)026:254: rin po che sna tshogs las grub pa'i gzhal yas khang bskyed pa'i sngags so //
NK015(ba)026:255: gong gi b+hi shud+d+he rnam par dag pa ni /
NK015(ba)026:256: brtsigs pa lnga rim rang kha ma yin zhing /
NK015(ba)026:257: ye shes lnga'i ngo bo la dgongs pa yin no //
NK015(ba)026:258: gdul bya'i dgos 'dod skong ba'i rtags su rina po che sna tshogas las grub pa'i gzhal yasa khang /
NK015(ba)026:259: chos kyi dbyings kyi ranga bzhina meda pa'i rtags su rgya khyon tshad bzunga du med pa /
NK015(ba)026:260: 'khor ba ma spangs 'bras bu lhun gyis grub cing yon tan rgyas pa'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)026:262: ye shes lnga rdzogs pa'i rtags su brtsigs pa nang nas rim pa bzhin sngon po /
NK015(ba)026:267: de yang me long ye shes 'gag med du shar
NK015(ba)026:268: zhing 'gro ba'i rgyud la 'chos 'khor bskor ba'i rtags
NK015(ba)026:269: su / shar logas 'khora lo dkar posa brgyan pa /
NK015(ba)026:270: mnyam nyid ye shes yon tan rdzogs shing gdul bya'i re ba skong ba'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)026:271: lhor ser po rin po che /
NK015(ba)026:272: sor rtogs ye shes chos spyi dang rang gis mtshan nyid mkhyen cing /
NK015(ba)026:273: mtha'i skyon gyis ma gos pa'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)026:275: bya grub ye shes phrin las sna tshogs kyis bdag
NK015(ba)026:276: gzhan gyi don gnyis lhun gyis grub pa'i rtags su
NK015(ba)026:278: chos dbyings ye shes kyis phar la thams cad 'joms
NK015(ba)026:279: shing tshur la gang gis mi tshugs pa'i ngo bo
NK015(ba)026:280: la 'gyur ba med pa'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)026:281: steng mthinga naga gis rdo rje pho gyo mo gyo
NK015(ba)026:282: chos nyid mi 'gyur ba yon tan gzhan la dpag
NK015(ba)026:283: pa'i rtags su / brtsigs pa'i steng du gser las grub pa'i pha gu gnyis sna gcig 'geb /
NK015(ba)026:284: bden pa gnyis dbyer med pa'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)026:285: pha gu la chun 'phyang rin po che'i phreng ba rgyus pa'i d+r+wa ba yod pa /
NK015(ba)026:286: chun 'phyang ni mdzes gdung la yod par bzhed do //
NK015(ba)026:287: thabs ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)026:288: pha gu'i nang brtsigs pa'i kha chod rnams thog na
NK015(ba)026:289: ka thung nyer brgyad kyi bar dpung lhas kyis sbrel
NK015(ba)026:290: ba'i steng na mdzes gdung la rin po che'i shar
NK015(ba)026:292: yang na shar bu ni phyi rtse'i snar yod par yang bzhed do //
NK015(ba)026:293: mda' yab shel gyi mchod rten gyi bar thams cad la gdugs dang /
NK015(ba)026:295: ba dan sna tshogs sgreng ba /
NK015(ba)026:296: yang na mda' yab rin po che'i thong por 'dod yang zer /
NK015(ba)026:297: thugs rje dang sprul pa'i 'phro 'du rgyun ma chad pa'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)026:298: mdzes gdung gis thog na phyam rtsa nyer brgyad yod
NK015(ba)026:299: pa'i snar seng mgo yod pa'i kha nas mu tig
NK015(ba)026:300: gi d+r+wa ba dang d+r+wa ba phyed pa 'phyang ba
NK015(ba)026:301: la drila bu rnga yab dang zur gyi dril bu
NK015(ba)026:302: chen po la rnga yab chena po'i bsila yaba 'phyo
NK015(ba)026:303: ba / bsnyen gnas brgyad rdzogs pa'i rtags su ka gdan dang /
NK015(ba)026:304: 'phags lam brgyad rdzogs pa'i rtags su ka ba dang /
NK015(ba)026:305: rnam thar brgyad rdzogs pa'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)026:306: ka rgyan dang ka gzhu rnams rin po che 'abra ba lasa byas pa phyogs mdog /
NK015(ba)026:307: mi 'jigs pa bzhi dang ldan pa'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)026:308: ka ba'i thog na gdung bzhi mig mang ris su bris pa /
NK015(ba)026:309: stong nyid bco brgyad phar phyin bcu rdzogs pa'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)026:310: phyam rtsa rin po che'i gdung phran nyer brgyad phyogs bzhir bzhi bzhi /
NK015(ba)026:312: stobs bcu ma 'dres pa bco brgyad dang ldan pa'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)026:313: phyam rtse gdung thung nyer brgyad kyis mthud pa /
NK015(ba)026:314: 'dod yon lnga ma spangs rnam dag rgyan du rdzogs pa'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)026:315: 'dod yon gyi lha mo dpag med phyogs bcur 'khrigs pa /
NK015(ba)026:316: bsgom dbang du kha khyer la bsgom /
NK015(ba)026:317: sngar gyi bshad srol kha cig la /
NK015(ba)026:318: gong gi pha gu'i steng du mchod snam dmar po
NK015(ba)026:319: gyang gzhung bskyang ba lta bu yod par 'dod pa
NK015(ba)026:320: snang yang / tshul de ni bri bsgom 'chad gsum gang dang yang mi mthun ste /
NK015(ba)026:321: bri ba'i dbang du thig dang mi mthun ste mchod
NK015(ba)026:322: snam gyi phyi na pha gu yod dgos pa'i phyir
NK015(ba)026:323: dang / bsgom pa'i dbang du mi mthun pa ni /
NK015(ba)026:324: dmar cha steng du song bas 'chi ba rnyed pa dang /
NK015(ba)026:325: 'chad pa'i dbang du mi mthun pa ni /
NK015(ba)026:326: las rlung gis ye shes kyis rlung mnan pas nam
NK015(ba)026:327: yang lam du mi 'gyur ba'i skyon rnams yod cing
NK015(ba)026:328: / gang dang yang mi mthun pas spang bar bya'o //
NK015(ba)026:329: chos rje zur pa tshang gis bzhed pa la /
NK015(ba)026:330: mchod snam gyi phyi na pha gu yod par 'dod de /
NK015(ba)026:335: ka thung bcu drug gi phrag /
NK015(ba)026:336: d+r+wa ba d+r+wa phyed kyi gseb na mchod pa'i lha mo rnams kyi mchod pa 'bul bar bsgom te /
NK015(ba)026:337: de yang gzugs kyi lha mo dkar mos me long bsnams pa dang /
NK015(ba)026:338: sgra'i lha mo sngon mos phyag na pi wang bsnams pa /
NK015(ba)026:339: dri'i lha mo ljang kus phyag na dri'i dung chos thogs pa /
NK015(ba)026:340: ro'i lha mo dmar mos phyag na mkhar gzhung g.yos kyis bkang ba thogs pa /
NK015(ba)026:341: reg bya'i lha mo'i phyag na na bza' pan tsa li ka thogs pa 'khrigs pa'o //
NK015(ba)026:342: theg pa lnga rdzogs pa'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)026:343: bya skyib lnga dang ldan pa /
NK015(ba)026:344: chos nyid 'gyur ba med pa mtshon pa'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)026:345: bya skyib kyis dbus gtso bo'i thog tu dar mthing nag gis bla re /
NK015(ba)026:346: thabs dang shes rab mtshon pa'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)026:347: bya skyib kyi 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi dod pa'i rtse
NK015(ba)026:348: mo nas nyi zla 'khrug pa'i skar khung lding ba
NK015(ba)026:349: / ye shes phra men du ma mtshon pa'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)026:350: thog gi bang rim gyi mtshams rnams su skar tshogs gsal ba /
NK015(ba)026:352: sangs rgyas gsang bas phyi dbyibs mchod rten mkhar thabs dang /
NK015(ba)026:353: rgyal khab ri bo gur du 'dod //
NK015(ba)026:354: ces dbyibs la lnga yod pa'i mchod rten /
NK015(ba)026:355: de la brgyad yod pa'i nang nas byang chub chen po'i mchod rten ltar du bshad na /
NK015(ba)026:359: dbang po lnga mtshon pa'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)026:362: bum pa byang chub kyi lam yan lag bdun /
NK015(ba)026:365: 'khor lo stobs bcu rnam thar gsum dang bcu gsum /
NK015(ba)026:366: gdugs thugs rje chen pos gdul bya nyon mongs pa'i tsha gdung las skyobs /
NK015(ba)026:368: de la dril bu 'phyang ba stong nyid kyi sgra /
NK015(ba)026:369: gdugs kyi thog gis nyi zla ni thabs shes rab /
NK015(ba)026:370: nang na gtso bo gang byed kyi thugs phyag mtshan gyis mtshan pa la /
NK015(ba)026:371: rdo rje'i tog ni mi nub bstan pa'i rgyal mtshan no //
NK015(ba)026:372: de ting kun ting phyag rgya gcig spros kyi rnam thar sgo bzhi nas 'jug pa'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)026:373: gzhal yas khang gis phyogs bzhir sgo bzhi ni rgya sgo lta bu ma yin sgo khyud can no //
NK015(ba)026:374: ma rig pa'i mun pa la ye shes kyis mthong khong gsal ba'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)026:375: sgo khong sgo srung gi khang pa mun nag gi
NK015(ba)026:376: grib so 'khrigs pa la bcu gcig do rje'i 'gring
NK015(ba)026:378: 'khor ba la rnam par thar pa'i theg pa brgyad bsgrod pa'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)026:379: sgo them rta bab phyi bzhi nang bzhi /
NK015(ba)026:380: rang sa'i 'bras bu brgyad thob pa'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)026:382: rta rkang chu skyes rin chen sgrom //
NK015(ba)026:383: ma skyes thabs kyis za ra tshags //
NK015(ba)026:385: sna tshogs khyung mgo rim par 'khrigs //
NK015(ba)026:389: rdzu 'phrul rkang bzhi rim pa ltar mtshon pa'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)026:390: sgo khang phyi zur bzhi po nas rta bab kyis ka gdan dang /
NK015(ba)026:391: bum pa las byung ba'i ka ba ka zhu rnams rin po che las grub pa phyogs mdog /
NK015(ba)026:395: lam dang bden bzhi'i bsam gtan mtshon pa'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)026:396: rta bab kyi gdung ring gnyis la gdung thung gnyis
NK015(ba)026:397: kyi sna la chu srin gyi zhal gnyis yod pas
NK015(ba)026:398: bzungs te / ta ra ni rta bab /
NK015(ba)026:399: na yisa ni chu srin ste bzungsa pa'i don yang de bzhin no //
NK015(ba)026:402: sgo khang nang gi rgyan dgu dang /
NK015(ba)026:405: brda drug gis bshad pa yod pa las /
NK015(ba)026:406: gzhan rnams logs su shes la /
NK015(ba)026:407: 'dir brda drug dang rgyan dgu bshad na /
NK015(ba)026:408: rta bab steng gi chos 'khor ni gtso bo'i barda'o //
NK015(ba)026:410: 'og gi dbus kyi gtso bo chen po ni rgyab
NK015(ba)026:411: nas lta dus sgo nang du snang ba'i tshul ni
NK015(ba)026:413: 'khor lo'i thog gis gdugs mdun rgyab g.yas g.yon du dar dpyang bzhi 'phyang ba la /
NK015(ba)026:414: gnyis la g+han+d+he gnyis phyang ba ni drang don gyi brda /
NK015(ba)026:415: dar lce gnyis la rdo rje dril bu gnyis btags pa ni thabs shes rab kyis barda'o //
NK015(ba)026:416: sgo khang gi rgyan dgu ni /
NK015(ba)026:417: smad na nyon mongs zil gyis gnon pa la /
NK015(ba)026:418: gti mug non cing stobs bcu mtshon pa la glang chen /
NK015(ba)026:419: zhe sdang non cing mi 'jigs pa bzhi mtshon pa'i seng+ge /
NK015(ba)026:420: 'dod chags non cing tshad med bzhi mtshon pa'i ngang pa /
NK015(ba)026:421: bar na las rnams so sor 'byed pa la /
NK015(ba)026:422: ri dwags snying rje dang ldan pas sdig las mi byed pas g.yo ba dang /
NK015(ba)026:423: khyi'u chung bzod pa dang ldan pa'i dge sdig gis
NK015(ba)026:424: bya ra byed pas legs nyes srang la gtegs shing
NK015(ba)026:426: steng na sdug bsngal ma spangs dang du len pa la /
NK015(ba)026:427: nyon mongs ye shes su shar ba'i phyir klu /
NK015(ba)026:428: de nyid thugs rjes 'dzin shes la gtor mi shes pa'i phyir chu srin /
NK015(ba)026:429: lta ba chos nyid du shar ba'i byin rlabs kyis
NK015(ba)026:430: des khyung gis klu rgyal las blong ba bzhin no
NK015(ba)026:432: ye nas mnyam pa nyid la mi 'da' bas nyon
NK015(ba)026:433: mongs gtan nas mi skye ba mtshon pa'i rtags su
NK015(ba)026:434: / ta la'i ljon shanga mgo bo bcad zin brgyad dam bcu drug /
NK015(ba)026:435: man ngag ltar na mkha' 'gro sum cu so gnyis kyis gdan yin pas so gnyis su 'dod gsungs /
NK015(ba)026:436: gdul bya'i re ba yid la bsam pa bzhin du skong bar mtshon pa'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)026:437: dapaga bsam shinga la rina po che'i tsong tsonga gis
NK015(ba)026:438: spras la dril bu g.yer kha'i brgyan pa ta la'i
NK015(ba)026:440: de dag gis bar du rin po che'i pha wang dang /
NK015(ba)026:441: khrus kyi rdzing bu yang ta la dang dpag bsam shing gis grangs ltar yod do /
NK015(ba)026:443: / 'khor ba'i chos thams cad la dbang bsgyur ba mtshon pa'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)026:447: de'i nang na me tog ltum zeng dkar po'i tshal gyi steng du /
NK015(ba)026:448: dad pa can gtam nyan pa'i 'khor /
NK015(ba)026:449: 'jig rten gyi lha chen po la sogs dpal mgon rnams kyi gdan no //
NK015(ba)026:450: rang rig pa'i ye shes 'ba' zhig tu snang ba'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)026:451: nang dang phyi rol lta bu ma yin te /
NK015(ba)026:452: kun tu yang nang du gyur pa'o /
NK015(ba)026:455: chos dbyings ye shes spros dang bral ba'i rtags su lte ba zlum po /
NK015(ba)026:456: de nyid ye shes bzhir snang ba'i rtags su rtsibsa bzhi /
NK015(ba)026:457: ye shes bzhir snang dus chos dbyings ye shes las ma g.yos pa'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)026:458: rdo rje mu khyud kyis bskor ba /
NK015(ba)026:459: de nyid zhi ba phyogs gcig par lhung ba ma yin te /
NK015(ba)026:460: che ba'i yon tan rgyas pa'i rtags su gru bzhi /
NK015(ba)026:461: ye shes re re la yang ye shes bzhi bzhi
NK015(ba)026:462: shar ba'i rtags su glo 'bur makhara thabsa bzhisa brgyan
NK015(ba)026:463: pa / bden gnyis ya ma bral ba'i rtags su lha snam kun tu 'khor ba /
NK015(ba)026:464: theg pa gzhan las 'dir bla na med pa'i theg pas 'phags shing der bgrod pa'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)026:465: lha snam nas lte ba'i bar la rdo rje'i 'gring bu re re'am /
NK015(ba)026:466: khru re re'i mtho dman du yod pa'o //
NK015(ba)026:468: 'og gzhi chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i gdan dang /
NK015(ba)026:469: smon lam gus pa'i gdan dang /
NK015(ba)026:470: yon tan gyi che bas nyes tshogs bcoms pa'i gdan dang /
NK015(ba)026:471: sa'i khyad par bgrod pa'i gdan dang /
NK015(ba)026:472: thugs rig pa rang snang gis gdan no //
NK015(ba)026:474: chos 'khor rgyun chad med pa bskor ba'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)026:476: gnyis pa smon lam gus pa'i gdan ni /
NK015(ba)026:477: sa mtha'i byang sems smon lam gyi dbang gis seng+ge
NK015(ba)026:478: la sogs par sprul nas lus gdan du phul nas
NK015(ba)026:479: nyon sgrib sbyangs / rna bas chos nyan nas shes sgrib sbyangs bar 'dod /
NK015(ba)026:480: gsum pa yon tan gyi nyes tshogs bcom pa'i gdan ni /
NK015(ba)026:481: shes rab rang bzhin med pa'i rtags su nyi ma /
NK015(ba)026:482: thabs 'gag pa med pa'i rtags su zla ba /
NK015(ba)026:483: thugs la nyes pa'i skyon dang bral ba'i rtags su pad+ma /
NK015(ba)026:484: gdul bya'i re ba dgos 'dod lhun gyi grub pa'i rtags su rin po che'i khri rkang /
NK015(ba)026:485: de yang dkor bdun ngo bo nyid lhun gyi grub
NK015(ba)026:486: pa'i rtags su khri rkang re re la mdzod mig
NK015(ba)026:488: lnga pa thugs rig pa rang snang ba'i gdan ni /
NK015(ba)026:489: sangs rgyas kyis dgongs par 'bras bu'i chos rnams lhun
NK015(ba)026:490: grub tu rdzogs pa'i rtags su sems can lnga'i gdan
NK015(ba)026:491: du snang ste / mi 'jigas pa bzhi'i rtagsa seng+ge /
NK015(ba)026:493: rdzu 'phrula gyi rkang pa bzhi'i rtagsa rta /
NK015(ba)026:495: phrin lasa bzhi'i rtagsa shanga shanga /
NK015(ba)026:496: de rnams re re la'ang brgyad brgyad re kh+aa phyogs bzhir blta ba /
NK015(ba)026:497: khyi tshugs su sdod nas ro stod kyi khri btegs pa'i tshul du 'dod /
NK015(ba)026:499: skyes bu lnga la lnga brtsegs pa ste /
NK015(ba)026:500: sems dpa' la ni sum brtsegs so //
NK015(ba)026:501: nyi rkyang khro la pad rkyang thub /
NK015(ba)026:502: kun bzang yab yum bzhi brtsegs so //
NK015(ba)026:505: sgo ba la nyi pad gnyis brtsegs /
NK015(ba)026:506: kun bzang yab yum dkyil 'khor la dgod pa'i tshe gsum brtsegs dang /
NK015(ba)026:507: chos 'chad pa'i tshe lnga brtsegs su bshad do //
NK015(ba)026:508: gdan gyi steng du zla ba 'ong ba'i rgyu mtshan ni /
NK015(ba)026:509: gsang snying 'grel ba mang du snang yang /
NK015(ba)026:511: zhi ba'i lha kun la zla ba steng du 'ong la /
NK015(ba)026:512: khro bo'i lha kun la nyi ma steng du 'ong zhes bshad do //
NK015(ba)026:513: mu tig gis d+r+wa ba'i khri khebs ni dam pa'i zhal gzigs yin gsungs /
NK015(ba)026:514: rten bskyed pa'i skabs 'dir 'og gzhi 'byung ba lnga yang ye shes lnga /
NK015(ba)026:515: nang gi gdan 'khor lo yang ye shes lnga /
NK015(ba)026:516: brtsigs pa yang ye shes lnga /
NK015(ba)026:517: brtsigs pa'i rgyab na yod pa'i phyag mtshan lnga yang ye shes lngar bshad pas bldab bam zhe na /
NK015(ba)026:519: dkyil 'khor la gzhi lam 'bras bu tshang ba dang /
NK015(ba)026:520: lha la gdan gsum 'dzom dgos gsungs te /
NK015(ba)026:521: de la 'og gzhi 'byung ba lnga'i ye shes lnga ni /
NK015(ba)026:522: gzhi'i ye shes lnga yin la /
NK015(ba)026:523: gdan 'khor los ye shes lnga mtshon pa ni lam yin la /
NK015(ba)026:524: brtsigs pa dang de la dod pa'i phyag mtshan ni 'bras bu'i ye shes yin te /
NK015(ba)026:525: de la brtsigs pa'i ye shes ni /
NK015(ba)026:526: bdag don rtags pa'i ye shes lnga yin la /
NK015(ba)026:527: phyag mtshan gyi ye shes ni gzhan don du snang tshul gyi ye shes lnga mtshon no //
NK015(ba)026:529: dbus na sangs rgyas rigs lnga'i gdan /
NK015(ba)026:530: bar na sems dpa' sems ma'i gdan /
NK015(ba)026:531: sgo na khro bo khro mo'i gdan no //
NK015(ba)026:532: da ni brten pa lha bskyed pa'i cho 'phrul ni /
NK015(ba)026:533: a dkar po las k+sha sngon po byung /
NK015(ba)026:534: a dang k+sha'i khyad para lasa /
NK015(ba)026:535: dur mo dang rdo gnyis 'phrad pa bzhin du /
NK015(ba)026:536: yi ge bzhi bcu gnyis su byung ste /
NK015(ba)026:537: so so'i gdan thog tu bab pa las /
NK015(ba)026:538: yab rnams kyis yi ge ni /
NK015(ba)026:539: thabs 'gag med mtshon pa'i rtags su yi ge log po yin la /
NK015(ba)026:540: yum rnams kyi yi ge ni dbyings 'gyur ba med pa mtshon pa'i rtags su drang yig yin no //
NK015(ba)026:541: gsung yig 'bru bsgom tshar nas kha bskang ba ni /
NK015(ba)026:543: semas can ngaga gi sgrib pa ni thun mong du bzhi /
NK015(ba)026:544: khyad par du brtags pa mngon par zhen pa'i sgrib pa sbyangsa /
NK015(ba)026:545: slar tshur 'dus yongas su gyur pa lasa /
NK015(ba)026:546: phyag mtshan bzhi bcu gnyis su gyur /
NK015(ba)026:547: de nas thugs phyag mtshan gzhung bzhin du bsgom la /
NK015(ba)026:550: semsa can yida kyis thun mong du gsum /
NK015(ba)026:551: khyad par du gang zag gi bdag tu 'dzin pa'i sgrig pa sbyangsa /
NK015(ba)026:552: tshur 'dus yongas su gyur pa lasa /
NK015(ba)026:553: phra mo bzhi bcu gnyis su gyur /
NK015(ba)026:554: de la sku phra mo tshon gang ba bzhi bcu gnyis su gyur /
NK015(ba)026:556: semas can lus kyi thun mong du gsum /
NK015(ba)026:557: khyad par du chos la bdag tu 'dzin pa'i sgrib pa sbyangsa /
NK015(ba)026:558: tshur 'dus yongas su gyur pa lasa /
NK015(ba)026:559: yongas rdzogsa bzhi bcu gnyis su gyura /
NK015(ba)026:560: h'u rgyu ma nor brtse ba'i sngags /
NK015(ba)026:561: badz+ra d+h+rika ni rdo rje sems dpa' mthing ka rdo rje 'dzin pa bskyed pa rkyen gyi sngags /
NK015(ba)026:562: rtsa sngags dang bskyed sngags gnyis sbrel ba ni bzlas pa las sngags so //
NK015(ba)026:563: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi sngags lhag ma kun la de ltar du shes so //
NK015(ba)026:564: yongs rdzogs zhe gnyis la don rtags sbyar nas bshad na /
NK015(ba)026:565: de yang gzhan rnams rtogs pa dang sbyar /
NK015(ba)026:566: yid chos thub pa drug dag pa dang sbyar gsungs pas /
NK015(ba)026:567: dbus su rdo rje semas dapa'a chosa dbyingsa ye shes lasa byung ba'i tshul ni /
NK015(ba)026:568: rnam shes phung po 'di gzhi gdod ma nas bcos
NK015(ba)026:569: slad dang bral ba chos dbyings snang stong gi mtha'
NK015(ba)026:570: gang du'ang mi bskyod pas mi bskyod pa thugs chos
NK015(ba)026:571: dbyings la 'gyur ba med pa'i phyir sku mdoga mthinga
NK015(ba)026:572: ga / dgongs pa skye 'jig dang bral ba'i rtags su phyag mtshan rdo rje /
NK015(ba)026:573: shar gyi rtsibsa steng du me longa ye shes lasa byung ba'i tshul ni /
NK015(ba)026:574: gzugs kyi phung po bcos slad dang bral ba de
NK015(ba)026:575: nyid rang gsal ba la cir yang snang ba'i rnama
NK015(ba)026:576: par snang madzada sku dri ma dang bral ba'i phyir
NK015(ba)026:577: dakara po / sku'i sgo nas sems can gyi don
NK015(ba)026:578: mdzad nas chos 'chad dgos pa'i rtags su phyag na
NK015(ba)026:579: dakara po / 'khora lo / lho rina 'byung mnyam nyid ye shesa lasa byung ba'i tshul ni /
NK015(ba)026:580: tshor phung 'di gnas su dag nas tshor ba yul
NK015(ba)026:581: du gsal ba dang stong pa dbyer med pa las
NK015(ba)026:582: sangs rgyas kyi yon tan kun 'byung bas rina chen
NK015(ba)026:583: 'byung ldan / yon tan la dgos 'dod 'byung ba'i phyir ser po /
NK015(ba)026:584: yon tan gyi sgo nas gdul bya'i re ba skongs pa'i rtags su phyag na rina po che /
NK015(ba)026:585: nub tu snang ba mtha'a yas so sora rtogsa pa'i ye shesa las byung ba'i tshul ni /
NK015(ba)026:586: 'du shes kyi phung po gnas su dag nas /
NK015(ba)026:587: 'du shes kyis shes bya'i yul so sor ma 'dres par gsal ba ste /
NK015(ba)026:588: zhing khams mthar thug pa med par gsal bas snang
NK015(ba)026:589: ba mtha' yas gsung so sor rtogs pa'i mtha' gnyis
NK015(ba)026:590: dbang du bsdu ba'i phyir damra po /
NK015(ba)026:591: gsung gis sgo nas sems can gyi don byas kyang
NK015(ba)026:592: nyes skyon gyi ma gos pa'i rtags su phyag na
NK015(ba)026:593: pad+ma / byang du don yod grub pa'i ye shes lasa byung ba'i tshul ni /
NK015(ba)026:594: 'du byed kyi phung po la sna tshogs su snang
NK015(ba)026:595: dus chos nyid rang las ma g.yos pa bzhin du
NK015(ba)026:596: / 'khor ba ma stongs gis bar du gzhan don
NK015(ba)026:597: gyi phrin las rgyun mi 'chad cing lam bar ma
NK015(ba)026:598: dor chud mi za bar 'bras bu la sbyor bas
NK015(ba)026:600: phrin las lhun gyi grub pa'i phyir ljang ku /
NK015(ba)026:601: bdag gzhan gyi don gnyis lhun grub tu 'byung ba'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)026:603: rigs lnga'i phyag g.yon gyi dbyings mtshon pa'i rtags su drila bu bsnamsa cing /
NK015(ba)026:604: g.yas kyi phyag mtshan dang bsnol nas yum la 'khyud pa ni /
NK015(ba)026:605: dbyingsa dang ye shesa dbyer meda pa'i rtagsa so //
NK015(ba)026:606: de yanga dabu gsum ltar na sku gsung thugs /
NK015(ba)026:608: thun mong khyad par gyi mtshan bzang dang dpe byad rnams kyi brgyan pa /
NK015(ba)026:610: spyod pa dang sras kyi 'byung khungs du gyur pa ste /
NK015(ba)026:611: de la yum lnga ni sras kyi 'byung khungs du gyur pa dang /
NK015(ba)026:613: nam mkha' ni stong pa ste /
NK015(ba)026:614: stong pas rnam shes bskyed cing /
NK015(ba)026:615: chos thams cad kyis 'byung gzhir gyur pas na nam mkha'a dbyibsa phyug ma /
NK015(ba)026:616: sa yis gzugs snang bskyed cing /
NK015(ba)026:617: rang la bzang ngan gyi rtog pa dang bral zhing
NK015(ba)026:618: snang dus stong bas na yum sangsa rgyas spyan ma
NK015(ba)026:619: dang gnyis su med par 'khril ba /
NK015(ba)026:621: tshor bas chos thams cad bskyed pas na yum m+aa ma k+ai dang gnyis su med par 'khril ba /
NK015(ba)026:622: mes gsal ba'i 'du shes bskyed cing /
NK015(ba)026:623: rtogs na gzung 'dzin gyi lhag pa las skyobs pa dang /
NK015(ba)026:624: srid pa'i ljan ljin skem par byed pas na yum
NK015(ba)026:625: gos dkar mo dang gnyis su med par 'khril ba
NK015(ba)026:626: / rlung gis 'du byed kyis las bskyed cing /
NK015(ba)026:627: phrin las kyis sems can sangs rgyas kyi sar sgrol
NK015(ba)026:628: ba la mi 'da' bas yum dam tshig sgrol ma
NK015(ba)026:629: dang gnyis su med par 'khril ba /
NK015(ba)026:630: yum de rnams kyi g.yas yab la 'khyud pa ni /
NK015(ba)026:631: dbyings ye shes dang dbyer med pa'i rtags /
NK015(ba)026:632: g.yon na rang rtags kyis phyag mtshan dril bu bsnams pa ni /
NK015(ba)026:633: stong pa dbyings kyis cha 'dzin pa'i don rtags so //
NK015(ba)026:634: yab yum bcu po de dag gis bzhugs tshul ni /
NK015(ba)026:639: yab yum gyi rdo rje dang pad+ma gnyis rtse mo
NK015(ba)026:640: sprad pa'i bde ba la rgyu 'bras kyi ris mnyam
NK015(ba)026:642: 'bras bu'i ming rgyu la btags pa ste /
NK015(ba)026:644: yab yum mnyam par bzhag pa la bdag gzhan gyi don mdzad pa thams cad rdzogs pa'i phyir /
NK015(ba)026:646: zhabs mthil gnyis barla'i steng du bton nas rdo rje'i
NK015(ba)026:647: lte ba'i tshul du gnas shing sor mo bcu rdo
NK015(ba)026:648: rje rwa'i tshul du byas pa ni /
NK015(ba)026:650: bde ba chen po'i spyod pas 'dul ba'i phyir bya
NK015(ba)026:651: ba ma yin pa brtul nas bya ba la zhugs
NK015(ba)026:653: yang na yab rdo rje'i skyil krung /
NK015(ba)026:655: zhabs gnyis yab la 'khyud cing zhabs mthil sbyar ba'o //
NK015(ba)026:656: yab yum bcu po ni longas sku'o /
NK015(ba)026:659: shar lho nas rim pa bzhin du nang gi ye shes sems dpa' yab yum gyi don rtags las /
NK015(ba)026:661: rnam shes bzhi'i thugs rjes cha yin te /
NK015(ba)026:662: mig gis rnam shes kyis gzugs mthong bar byed pa'i gzugs kyi snying po ste /
NK015(ba)026:664: de yanga sa'i snying po ni myu gu yin te /
NK015(ba)026:665: gzugs snang stong du chod nas /
NK015(ba)026:666: sku gsum gyi myu gu bskyed pa'i rtags su phyag na myu gu rtse gsum /
NK015(ba)026:667: rnam snang gis thugs la skyes pa'i phyir sku mdoga dakara po /
NK015(ba)026:668: rna ba'i rnam shes chos thams cad thos pas mthar
NK015(ba)026:669: thug gi 'bras bu don gnyis lhun grub skyed pa'i
NK015(ba)026:671: sgra grags stong du thos pas rdo rje'i sku thob pa'i rtags su phyag na rdo rje bsnams /
NK015(ba)026:672: don grub kyi thugs las skyes pa'i phyir sku mdoga ljang ku /
NK015(ba)026:673: sna'i rnam shes kyis dri tshor ba tsam yin pas na nam mkha'i snying po /
NK015(ba)026:674: de yang nam mkha'i snyings po ni stong nyid yin te /
NK015(ba)026:675: dri tshor stong du tshod pa'i stong nyid zab mo
NK015(ba)026:676: rtogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi yon tan 'byung zhing mtha'
NK015(ba)026:677: gnyis gcod pa'i rtags su phyag na ral gri /
NK015(ba)026:678: rin 'byung gi thugs las skyes pa yin pas ser po /
NK015(ba)026:679: lce'i rnam shes ni gsung gi snying po yin pas spyan ras gzigas /
NK015(ba)026:680: khams gsum gyi sems can gyi ma rig pas spyan
NK015(ba)026:681: ras nas mdangs ba rnams la thugs rjes dus rtag
NK015(ba)026:682: par gzigs pa'am / yang na dgongs pa chos dbyings
NK015(ba)026:683: du ma g.yos nas mtha' can du ma gzigs spyan
NK015(ba)026:684: ras la yul bral gyi ye shes kyis ngang du
NK015(ba)026:686: ro myong stong du chod pa la nyes pa'i skyon gyis ma gos pa'i rtags su phyag na pad+ma /
NK015(ba)026:687: snang mtha'i thugs las skyes pa yin pa'i phyir sku mdoga damra po /
NK015(ba)026:690: mig gis yul gzugs su snang ba ni /
NK015(ba)026:692: gzugs dbyibs kha dog gnyis kyi mig gis rnam shes bskyed cing /
NK015(ba)026:693: gzugs snang dus stong pa'i rtags su sgeg cing me longa 'dzina pa /
NK015(ba)026:694: rnam snang gi sku las byung ba'i phyir dakara mo /
NK015(ba)026:695: rna ba'i yul sgra ni gzhi ma nges pa las sna tshogs 'byung ba'i rtags su gara ma ste /
NK015(ba)026:696: sgra zin ma zin gnyis kyi rna ba'i rnam shes bskyed cing /
NK015(ba)026:697: sangs rgyas kyi phrin las ni phyogs gcig tu ma nges la sna tshogs su 'byung ba'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)026:698: rkang po'i gzhi ma nges pa la lag pa'i gar sna tshogs su bsgyur zhing gnas pa'o //
NK015(ba)026:699: don grub kyi sku las byung ba'i phyir sku mdoga ljang ku /
NK015(ba)026:700: sna'i yul dri la rgyun chad med pa'i phreng ba ma /
NK015(ba)026:701: dri la bzang ngan gnyis kyi sna'i rnam shes bskyed cing /
NK015(ba)026:702: sangs rgyas kyi yon tan la rgyun chad med pa'i rtags su phyag na phreng ba /
NK015(ba)026:703: rin 'byung gi sku las byung ba'i phyir sera mo /
NK015(ba)026:704: lce'i yul ro'i nus pa'i ngag gis sgra bskyed pas glu ma /
NK015(ba)026:705: ro drug gis lce'i rnam shes bskyed cing /
NK015(ba)026:706: gsung gis chos sgo du ma 'chad pa'i rtags su pi wang /
NK015(ba)026:707: snang mtha'i sku las byung ba'i phyir damra mo /
NK015(ba)026:708: rnam shes bzhis yul bzhi la spyad pas kyang yum yin no //
NK015(ba)026:709: gru chad bzhi la shar lho nas rim pa bzhin
NK015(ba)026:710: du phyi'i sems dpa' yab yum gyi don rtags ni
NK015(ba)026:711: / dbang po bzhi'i rnam shes kyis yul du brda sprad pa'i cha nas gsung yin te /
NK015(ba)026:712: mig gis dbang po la bzang ngan gyi rtog pa med pa'i phyir byamsa pa ste /
NK015(ba)026:713: sku'i sgo nas sems can thams cad la mi gnod
NK015(ba)026:714: cing phan gdags pas nyon mongs pa'i tsha gdung las
NK015(ba)026:715: skyob par byed pa'i rtags su phyag na klu shing
NK015(ba)026:716: dang g+han+d+he / phyi'i sems dpa' yab yum ni rigs 'dres pa'i phyir /
NK015(ba)026:717: byams pa yab yum dkar ser /
NK015(ba)026:718: rna ba'i dbang po la rnam shes skye zhing chos thos pas /
NK015(ba)026:719: des 'bras bu sangs rgyas pas sgrib sel ste /
NK015(ba)026:720: sgrib pa gsum po rnam par sel ba'i yon tan dang ldan pa'i rtags su phyag na po ti /
NK015(ba)026:722: sna'i dbang po la rnam shes skye ba des dri'i tshor ba bskyed /
NK015(ba)026:723: des chos thams cad bskyed cing ma 'dres yongs rdzogs su shar ba'i phyir kun tu bzang po /
NK015(ba)026:724: chos thams cad 'bras bu'i ngo bor rdzogs pa'i rtags su phyag na snye ma /
NK015(ba)026:726: lce'i dbang pos chos kyi sgra bskyed cing /
NK015(ba)026:727: de nyams su blangs pas spangs rtogs sam /
NK015(ba)026:728: 'bras bu dbyings dang ye shes mngon du byed pa'i
NK015(ba)026:729: phyir 'ajama dapala bdag gzhan gyi don gnyis lhun gyis
NK015(ba)026:730: grub pa'i phrin las phyogs thams cad du rgyas pa'i
NK015(ba)026:732: dus bzhi la dbang po bzhis spyad pas yum ste /
NK015(ba)026:733: khar sang de ring la sogs dus bzhi la spyad pa'o //
NK015(ba)026:734: de la dus 'das pa dpyid kyis dus su rlung
NK015(ba)026:735: sob ma khu rlangs sna tshogs lang ba'i phyir bdug
NK015(ba)026:736: pa ma / lus can bde bar gshegs pa'i sku
NK015(ba)026:737: ru gyur pa'i byang chub kyi dris tshims pa'i rtags
NK015(ba)026:739: da ltar dbyar gyi dus su rtsi shing me tog kun rgyas pa'i phyir me tog ma ste /
NK015(ba)026:740: mtshan dang dpe byad kyis yon tan rdzogs pa'i rtags su phyag na me tog gi gzhong pa /
NK015(ba)026:741: ma 'ongs pa ston gyis dus su snod bcud thams
NK015(ba)026:742: cad bkrag zhugs nas gsal ba'i phyir mar me ma
NK015(ba)026:743: ste / sems can ma rig pa'i mdangs bsal ba'i dus su /
NK015(ba)026:744: ye shes kyi sgron mar snang ba'i rtags su mara me bsnamsa pa /
NK015(ba)026:745: phyis 'byung ba dgun gyi dus ni grang bas dri chab ma ste /
NK015(ba)026:746: zag bcas kyi phung po lnga la zag med kyi
NK015(ba)026:747: phung po lnga'i dris khyab pa'i rtags su dri chab
NK015(ba)026:749: rnam shes rnam grol ye shes /
NK015(ba)026:753: 'du byed shes rab kyi phung po'o //
NK015(ba)026:754: semas dapa'a de rnams kyi dbu la rala pa dang /
NK015(ba)026:755: matshana bazanga dpe byad dang ldan pa /
NK015(ba)026:756: zhabsa thams cad phyed krung gis bzhugs pa /
NK015(ba)026:757: yaba yum zhala sbyor du gansa pa /
NK015(ba)026:758: sems dpa' de rnams kyis lam mthar ma phyin gyis
NK015(ba)026:759: bar du bdag gzhan gyi don bsgrub dgos pa'i tshul
NK015(ba)026:760: g.yon bskum / g.yas gdan la phab pa dang /
NK015(ba)026:761: yab rnams kyi g.yon dril bu dang bcas pas yum la 'khyud pa /
NK015(ba)026:762: thugsa rjes semsa can thamsa cada la bu gcig la mas byamsa pa bzhina du semsa te /
NK015(ba)026:763: yab yum de rnams ni mngon byang gi sku'o //
NK015(ba)026:764: lha snam gyi shar du yid 'gyu ba rang grol
NK015(ba)026:765: nas yid 'dzin dag pas rtog tshogs rgyal ba'i dkyil
NK015(ba)026:766: 'khor du shar bas spyod yul thams cad sku dang
NK015(ba)026:767: ye shes su snang bas rgyud thams cad kyi byed
NK015(ba)026:768: pa po kun du bazanga po /
NK015(ba)026:769: bdag don du chos nyid mnyam pa nyid skye 'jig
NK015(ba)026:770: dang bral ba'i rtags su phyag manyama bzhag gisa steng
NK015(ba)026:771: na rdo rje dakara po rtse lnga pa ye shes
NK015(ba)026:773: chos sku la 'gyur ba med pa'i rtags su sku mdog sngon po /
NK015(ba)026:774: mkhyen pas shes bya'i dngos po thams cad chos dbyings
NK015(ba)026:775: su gzigs pa'i rtags su zhal nub tu gazigs pa
NK015(ba)026:776: / nub tu chosa 'dus byas dang 'dus ma byas
NK015(ba)026:777: thamsa cada snang bzhin ngo bo ma grub par gansa
NK015(ba)026:778: su dag pa'i rtagsa su yum kun tu bazanga mo
NK015(ba)026:779: / / shes bya'i baga chagas byang ba'i rtagsa su sku mdoga dkar mo /
NK015(ba)026:780: chos dbyings thams cad kyi 'byung khungs su gyur pa'i rtags su phyag na chosa 'byung /
NK015(ba)026:781: yab yum de gnyis ni chos kyi sku yina te /
NK015(ba)026:783: gyan cha rnams ni rigs lnga dang 'dra'o //
NK015(ba)026:785: bshad rgyud bla ma ltar na /
NK015(ba)026:786: kun dge slong gis cha byad can /
NK015(ba)026:787: shar lhor nga rgyal ma spangs gnas su dag pa'i rtags su /
NK015(ba)026:788: lha'i thub pa sku mdoga dakara po phyag na pi wang 'dzina pa /
NK015(ba)026:790: mi'i thub pa sku mdoga sera po phyag na bsreg shang dang para bu bsnamsa pa /
NK015(ba)026:791: lho nub tu phrag dog ma spangs /
NK015(ba)026:792: lha ma yina gyi thub pa sku mdoga ljang nag phyag gayasa rala gri /
NK015(ba)026:794: nub byang du gti mug ma spangs /
NK015(ba)026:795: byol songa gisa thub pa gsera gyi mdoga cana spyi bos chos kyi glegs bama khura ba /
NK015(ba)026:796: byang du ser sna ma spangs /
NK015(ba)026:797: yi dwagas gi thub pa sku mdoga ljang ser /
NK015(ba)026:798: phyag na rina po che'i za ma tog bsnamsa nas /
NK015(ba)026:799: yi dwagas thamsa cad la mchod sbyin gtong ba /
NK015(ba)026:800: byang shar du zhe sdang ma spangs /
NK015(ba)026:801: dmyal ba'i thub pa sku mdog nag po /
NK015(ba)026:802: phyag gayasa na me bsnamsa nas grang ba'i sdug bsngal sel bar byed pa /
NK015(ba)026:803: g.yon na chu bsnamsa nas tsha ba'i sdug bsngal sel bar byed pa /
NK015(ba)026:805: shar lho lha la lho phyogs mi //
NK015(ba)026:806: lho nub nub byang yi dwags byol //
NK015(ba)026:807: byang dang byang shar lha min dmyal //
NK015(ba)026:810: thub pa de rnams ni sprul pa'i sku yin te /
NK015(ba)026:811: 'gro ba'i dona la thugas bsnyil ba mi mang'a bar don mdzad pa'i rtagsa su /
NK015(ba)026:812: gadna pad+ma'i steng na bzhengas pa'o //
NK015(ba)026:813: sgo bzhir khro bo yab yum bskyed pa ni /
NK015(ba)026:814: de la lus kyi chos bzhi 'jom pa'i dus su /
NK015(ba)026:815: rtog pa gzhan rnams 'jig pas khro bo dang sbyar ba yin ste /
NK015(ba)026:816: gsang ba'i rnam shes kyi bde ba myong tsa na
NK015(ba)026:817: tha mal gyi rnam shes 'jig pas shar sgo thugs
NK015(ba)026:818: gshina rje gsheda / thugs bde 'dzin gyi dri ma dang bral ba'i rtags su thod skam /
NK015(ba)026:819: gsang ba'i yum pad+ma ni bde ba 'byung ba'i rten
NK015(ba)026:820: byed pas lho sgor stobsa po che sku skye 'jig
NK015(ba)026:822: gasnga ba'i dbang po'i bde ba brda sprad pas nub
NK015(ba)026:823: sgor gsung rta mgrina gsung gis nyon mongs pa bde
NK015(ba)026:824: ba rang ye shes su shar ba'i phyir pad+ma ste
NK015(ba)026:825: mi mgo rlon pa'i dbyug pa sbrul gyis dkris pa
NK015(ba)026:826: can no // gsum 'dus kyi reg pa yum gyi
NK015(ba)026:827: mkha' la byang sems 'khyil pa byang sgor bdud rtsi
NK015(ba)026:828: can no // 'khyil pa / phrin las bdud rtsi
NK015(ba)026:829: 'khril pas rang gzhan gyi don bsgrub pa'i rtags su
NK015(ba)026:831: rnams khro bo'i phyag mtshan yin pas dbyug par btsugs
NK015(ba)026:832: can no // 'khyil pa / rgya gram / te
NK015(ba)026:833: phyar ba'o // phyin ci log bzhir bzung bas 'khor
NK015(ba)026:834: ba'i lus kyi rtog pa bzhi bskyed cing /
NK015(ba)026:835: lta ngan bzhi dag pa'i khro mo ste /
NK015(ba)026:836: gsang ba'i rtog pa 'dul ba'i dus su rtog tshogs gzhan rnams 'dzin pa'i phyir /
NK015(ba)026:837: rtog pa rtag pa ma yina pa ni mi rtag pa dang /
NK015(ba)026:838: chag pa ma yina pa ni sdug bsngal ba dang /
NK015(ba)026:839: badga tu lta ba ma yin pa ni bdag med pa dang /
NK015(ba)026:840: matshana mara lta ba ma yina pa ni stong pa ste /
NK015(ba)026:841: bden bzhi chos nyid mngon du gyur pa'i dus na rtag par lta ba mi pham ma ste /
NK015(ba)026:842: rtag lta rang chos nyid 'gyur med rtag pa chen
NK015(ba)026:843: por rtogs pas khams gsum du mi 'khor bas mi
NK015(ba)026:844: pham cing / thams cad chos dbyings su bkug pa'i rtags su lcagsa kyu /
NK015(ba)026:845: chad par lta ba khro gnyer ma ni /
NK015(ba)026:846: chad lta dang rang chos nyid mtha' bral zung 'dzin
NK015(ba)026:847: gyi dri ma gtan nas chad par rtogs na khro
NK015(ba)026:848: gnyer ma ste / ye shes 'phel ba cher bskyang ba'i rtags su zhagsa pa /
NK015(ba)026:849: bdag tu lta ba ral gcig ma ni /
NK015(ba)026:850: bdag 'dzin rang byung gi ye shes rang snang nyag gcig tu rtog pas ral gcig ma ste /
NK015(ba)026:851: mtha' gnyis dbang du bsdu ba'i rtags su lcagsa sgrogsa /
NK015(ba)026:852: mtshan mar lta ba ro long ma ni /
NK015(ba)026:853: yul mtshan mar lta ba rang sku dang ye shes su rtogs pas ro lang ma ste /
NK015(ba)026:854: mtshan 'dzin thams cad chos kyi dbyings su 'jom pa'i rtags su dril bu bsnamsa pa /
NK015(ba)026:855: khro bo de dag ni rdo rje sku ste /
NK015(ba)026:856: dus gsum du gzigs phyir spyan gsum /
NK015(ba)026:857: skye bzhi rtsad nas gcod pa'i phyir mche ba bzhi brtsigsa pa /
NK015(ba)026:858: srid gsum chos dbyings su sgrol ba'i phyir g.yon na thod khrag yum la 'khyud pa /
NK015(ba)026:859: dapala chasa bcu drug ni dur khrod chas brgyad dang /
NK015(ba)026:866: thabs mkhas phrin las kyi gos zhing gi rked chings /
NK015(ba)026:867: khyab pa thugs rje'i gos glang chen gyi rko rlon stod g.yog /
NK015(ba)026:868: phyi nang gsang ba sdud pa'i gos stag sham mo //
NK015(ba)026:875: de dag ni rgyal byed dpa' rtags gis rgyan ste ru tra la phrog pa'o //
NK015(ba)026:877: gzi brjid 'bar ba chu srin brjid pa'i chas //
NK015(ba)026:878: thabs dang shes rab zung 'brel nyi zla'i chas //
NK015(ba)026:879: gdug pa can bsregs ye shes me'i chas //
NK015(ba)026:880: skye shi rtsad gcod mche ba zla tshes chas //
NK015(ba)026:881: khyab mdzad re skongs rdo rje gshogs pa'i chas //
NK015(ba)026:882: mnga' thang yongs rdzogs rdo rje lhag pa'i chas //
NK015(ba)026:883: sangs rgyas sar bgrod dbang gis bse khrab chas //
NK015(ba)026:884: gnod gdug bzlog byed rgya gram lcags kyis chas //
NK015(ba)026:885: ces de dag ni thugs rig pa rang snang gi chas so //
NK015(ba)026:886: khams lugs kyis dpal chas bcu drug ni logs su shes so //
NK015(ba)026:887: zhabs brkyang bskum du sgo bsrung ba'i tshul du /
NK015(ba)026:888: sangs rgyas gsang bas zur bltas su 'dod la /
NK015(ba)026:890: sgeg rdor gyis phyir blta bar bzhed do //
NK015(ba)026:891: lha tshogs de dag rnams la rang bzhin gyi sku mdog bzhi bzhi dang ldan ste /
NK015(ba)026:894: ku mu ta ltar snum la 'dril ba /
NK015(ba)026:895: dung ltar nyes pa'i skyon gyis ma gos pa'o //
NK015(ba)026:896: bde bar gshegs pa rnams bzhugs so //
NK015(ba)026:898: mnyen lcug 'khril ldem gzhon tshul can //
NK015(ba)026:904: ces lha thams cad zhi ba'i tshul dgu dang ldan pa ste /
NK015(ba)026:905: nga rgyal ma spangs gnas su dag pa'i rtags su yan lag gser zhun ma ltar mnyen pa /
NK015(ba)026:906: zhe sdang ma spangsa gnas su phyag sor sbrul mjug ltar lcug pa /
NK015(ba)026:907: 'dod chags ma spangs thabs shes g.yu'i ljon pa ltar phan tshun 'khril ba /
NK015(ba)026:908: gti mug sku sked thang shing ltar ldem pa /
NK015(ba)026:909: phrag dog byis pa lo brgyad pa ltar gzhona tshul can /
NK015(ba)026:910: thugs la ma rig pa med pa'i rtags su zla ba ltar gasla ba /
NK015(ba)026:911: che ba'i yon tan lhun gyi grub pa'i rtags su nyi ma ltar 'tshera ba /
NK015(ba)026:912: mtshan dpe yongs su rdzogs pa'i rtags su ri rgyal ltar lhun sdug pa /
NK015(ba)026:913: thams cad zil gyi non pa'i rtags su seng+ge 'bum gshib pa ltar gzi byin dang ldan pa /
NK015(ba)026:914: ba spu'i bu ga re re nas kyang gsal la rno ba'i 'od zer dkar /
NK015(ba)026:920: re re yang bye ba phrag drug drug 'phro ba'i tshogas chena po /
NK015(ba)026:921: khyad par du khro bo rnams kyis sku la me
NK015(ba)026:922: dpung 'abra ba'i phreng ba rdo rje rtse lnga pa'i
NK015(ba)026:923: rnam pa 'khrigsa pa'i 'oda kyis tshul can ste zhes
NK015(ba)026:924: pa'i / gzhal yas khang gis rgyab rdo rje rwa
NK015(ba)026:925: ba'i nang du zhing tshal ba'i gdan la mkha' 'gro
NK015(ba)026:926: so gnyis zur gyis bzhi ni pho yin gsungs /
NK015(ba)026:927: de rgyab tu dpal mgon bdun cu bsgom gsungs /
NK015(ba)026:928: gnyis pa dbang bskur ba'i cho 'phrul ni /
NK015(ba)026:929: de yang gang gis bskur na /
NK015(ba)026:932: lhag pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor zhe gnyis la /
NK015(ba)026:934: ye shes lnga'i chu rgyun gyis dbang bskur te /
NK015(ba)026:935: dgos ched gang gis phyir na /
NK015(ba)026:936: swa b+h+aa wa'i sgra dri ma dag par byed pa'i tshul ci ltar /
NK015(ba)026:937: theg pa 'og ma ltar spang gnyen gyi tshul du ma yin te /
NK015(ba)026:938: rang bzhin rtogs pa'i tshul gyis so //
NK015(ba)026:939: de yang rim pa ltar gung mo /
NK015(ba)026:944: gyen du brkyang ba'i rdo rje /
NK015(ba)026:945: sdom pa'i phyag rgya spyi bo la sogs pa'i gnas lngar gtug gam /
NK015(ba)026:946: yang na phyag rgya ma bcas kyang rung ste /
NK015(ba)026:947: dbu rgyan gyi sngags rnams rim par brjod pa'i tshe /
NK015(ba)026:948: rigs lnga yab yum rnams rim par sbyor ba mdzad pas /
NK015(ba)026:949: rjes chags kyis mes zhu ba stong pa nyid kyi
NK015(ba)026:950: ye shes la sogs ye shes lngas dbang bskur bas
NK015(ba)026:951: / nyon mongs pa lnga'i dri ma rim gyi dag nas /
NK015(ba)026:952: chu lud pa las rigs lngas dbu rim par brgyan par bsgom zhing /
NK015(ba)026:953: phung po lnga rnam dag rigs lnga thob pa'i ngo bo bdag yin snyam pa'i nga rgyal bar bya'o //
NK015(ba)026:954: de yang mi bskyod yab yum /
NK015(ba)026:956: thub drug gis dbu rgyan gyis gtso bo mi bskyod pa /
NK015(ba)026:960: gshin rje gshed yab yum la rnam snang /
NK015(ba)026:964: stobs po che yab yum la rin 'byung /
NK015(ba)026:968: rta mgrin yab yum la snang mtha' /
NK015(ba)026:972: bdud rtsi 'khyil pa yab yum la don grub /
NK015(ba)026:973: yang na kun la mi bskyod pas gtso bo byed par 'dod do //
NK015(ba)026:974: gsum pa byin gyis brlabs pa'i cho 'phrul ni /
NK015(ba)026:975: spyi bor glad pa dung khang gi nang du zla
NK015(ba)026:976: ba'i dkyil 'khor la gnas pa'i dkar po las 'od
NK015(ba)026:977: 'phros pas / de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs dam gyi rgyud bskul bas /
NK015(ba)026:978: sku'i byin gyis rlabs dbang thob /
NK015(ba)026:979: bdag de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku dang gnyis su med par byin gyis brlabs /
NK015(ba)026:980: rlob pa'i rtags su spyi bo'i zhu ba'i 'od phung las sku rdo rje gzhung bzhin du bskyed la /
NK015(ba)026:981: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis sku'i rang bzhin nga'am bdag yin no snyam pa'i nga rgyal bya'o /
NK015(ba)026:983: / 'og ma bzhi po de'i 'gres kyis shes par bya'o //
NK015(ba)026:984: lha de dag gis thugs kar ye shes sems dpa'
NK015(ba)026:985: rang rang dang 'dra ba'i phyag mtshan 'dzin 'dzin 'dra
NK015(ba)026:988: ye shes sems dpa'i de'i gdan yang /
NK015(ba)026:990: kun bzang la nyi la pad+ma gsum brtsegs /
NK015(ba)026:991: thub pa dang bzang mo la pad+ma /
NK015(ba)026:993: ye shes sems dpa' de'i thugs kar nyi ma'i steng
NK015(ba)026:994: du thugs phyag mtshan de la gsung yig 'bru'i mtshan
NK015(ba)026:996: bskyed pa'i sa bon +aa li k+aa li dang /
NK015(ba)026:997: sngags kyi yi ge dang pos mtshan pa gnyis las /
NK015(ba)026:998: 'dir phyag len la thub drug ma gtogs pa la sngags kyi yi ge dang pos mtshan la /
NK015(ba)026:999: thub drug la krem la sogs pa'o //
NK015(ba)026:1000: sgo ba yab la h'u bzhi /
NK015(ba)026:1001: yum la dza h'u bam ho bzhi'am phata bzhis mtshan pa /
NK015(ba)026:1002: de'i mtha' bskor du yab rnams la rang sngags /
NK015(ba)026:1003: nang nas klog pa'i tshul du g.yas bskor /
NK015(ba)026:1007: rin chen zur brgyad kyi nang /
NK015(ba)026:1010: yum lnga'i dril bu nang dril spo ba /
NK015(ba)026:1011: myu gu rtse gsum gyi 'dus mdo /
NK015(ba)026:1033: sreg shang yu ba'i bud mtshams /
NK015(ba)026:1034: me yar la 'bar chu mar la 'bab pa'i mtshams rnams su bsgom gsungs /
NK015(ba)026:1035: yang na yab thams cad la nyi ma /
NK015(ba)026:1036: yum thams cad la zla ba'i steng du /
NK015(ba)026:1037: rdo rje'i rigs thams cad la rdo rje h'u /
NK015(ba)026:1041: las kyi rigs thams cad la ral gri has mtshan pa /
NK015(ba)026:1042: sgo ba yab yum la rdo rje h'u gis mtshan pa 'dod pa yang snang /
NK015(ba)026:1043: byin gyis brlabs pa'i thugs lha dang /
NK015(ba)026:1044: ye shes sems dpa' bsgom tshul ni /
NK015(ba)026:1045: dam pa yab sras kyis ye shes sems dpa' dbus /
NK015(ba)026:1046: byin rlabs kyi lha ni thabs kyi cha yin pas g.yas su bsgom gsungs /
NK015(ba)026:1048: ye shes sems dpa' snying gi nang /
NK015(ba)026:1049: byin rlabs kyi lha snying gi rgya ba brang gi nang du bsgom gsungs /
NK015(ba)026:1050: bzhi pa ye shes pa rgyal ba'i dal bstims pa'i byin gyi brlabs pa dang /
NK015(ba)026:1051: mchod pa'i cho 'phrul la spyi don bcu bzhi ste /
NK015(ba)026:1052: dang po snyan gsan dbab pa ni /
NK015(ba)026:1053: de yang ma rtogs sems can gyi khams la ni /
NK015(ba)026:1054: log rtog rang snang gi dkyil 'khor rtog tshogs zhe gnyis su snang la /
NK015(ba)026:1055: rtogs pa sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa la ni /
NK015(ba)026:1056: ye shes rang snang gi dal rgyal ba zhe gnyis su snang la /
NK015(ba)026:1057: lam pa rnal 'byor pa la ni /
NK015(ba)026:1058: de nyid sems nyid rang snang gis dal lhag pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi dal du snang yang /
NK015(ba)026:1059: de gsum du chos dbyings su dbyer med yin pa'i phyir /
NK015(ba)026:1060: de bas rnal 'byor pa'i log rtog gi snang ba de /
NK015(ba)026:1061: ye shes kyi snang bar bya ba'i phyir /
NK015(ba)026:1062: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dal 'dir rdzogs pa
NK015(ba)026:1063: dang dus mnyam du bsam yas lhun grub mtha' dbus
NK015(ba)026:1064: med pa rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor du shar ba dang
NK015(ba)026:1065: dbyer med du bya ba'i phyir /
NK015(ba)026:1066: de yang gsang sngags lugs kyi sgo bzhi dang sbyar ba ni /
NK015(ba)026:1067: don dam gsal byed brjod pa tshig gis sgo /
NK015(ba)026:1068: mtshan ma brda rtags phyag rgya gar gyis sgo /
NK015(ba)026:1069: thugs dam gnad bskul gsang ba sngags kyi sgo /
NK015(ba)026:1070: dmigs pa rtse gcig ting 'dzin yid kyi sgo'o //
NK015(ba)026:1071: dang po brjod pa tshig gis ni /
NK015(ba)026:1073: phyag rgya ni rang gis dpung par se gol bsnol ma gdab ste /
NK015(ba)026:1075: badz+ra sa ma na dza h'u dza ces brjod la /
NK015(ba)026:1077: bsam yas lhun grub kyi rgyal ba rnams chos kyi
NK015(ba)026:1078: sku las gzugs kyi skur bzhengs nas zhal gyis phyogs
NK015(ba)026:1080: thugs kyis dgongs nas byon ma rag par bsam la /
NK015(ba)026:1081: ja 'dren gyi tshul du yid kyis mchod pa 'bul /
NK015(ba)026:1082: gnyis pa spyan drangs pa ni /
NK015(ba)026:1083: ho yoda meda ces brjod pas bsam yas lhun grub kyi dal spyan drangs te /
NK015(ba)026:1084: ngo bo la byon pa dang bzhud pa med kyang
NK015(ba)026:1085: gdul bya'i don du mar me gcig la gcig chad
NK015(ba)026:1086: pa lta bur byon nas me ri 'dab 'brel gyi
NK015(ba)026:1087: shar sgo dang shar sgo sprad nas bzhugs par bsgom
NK015(ba)026:1088: / gsum pa brten par bzhugs su gsol ba ni /
NK015(ba)026:1090: badz+ra sa ma ya dzasa sgo bzhi nas nang du spyan drangs /
NK015(ba)026:1091: sa ma ya h'u gis lha snam nas g.yas bskor
NK015(ba)026:1092: du byon nas dam tshig pa re re'i g.yas su
NK015(ba)026:1093: ye shes pa re re bzhugs par bsam /
NK015(ba)026:1094: sa ma ya s+t+wam gyis bstim /
NK015(ba)026:1095: sa ma ya hosa ye shes dam tshig dbyer med du gyur par bsgom /
NK015(ba)026:1096: bzhi pa sngon du 'gro ba phyag gis mchod pa ni /
NK015(ba)026:1098: phyogs bzhir lha mo spyan ma la sogs pa bzhi grangs dpag tu med pa spros pas /
NK015(ba)026:1099: sgo bzhi nas dgyes pa'i glu blang nas gsang ba'i phyag byed pa'am /
NK015(ba)026:1100: yang na lha re re la'ang lha mo bzhi bzhis bskor nas bstod par bsam la /
NK015(ba)026:1101: khro bo ltar phyag dngos su mi dgos gsungs /
NK015(ba)026:1102: tshar nas lha mo bzhi rang gis thugs kar bsdu'o //
NK015(ba)026:1103: lnga pa kun bzang mchod pa ni /
NK015(ba)026:1104: tshigs bcad brjod dus phyi nang gsang ba de kho na nyid dang bzhi'i don bsgom dgos te /
NK015(ba)026:1105: de la phyi'i mchod pa ni /
NK015(ba)026:1106: rgya mtsho thams cad yon chab /
NK015(ba)026:1107: rtsi shing nags tshal thams cad me tog lho sprin na bun thams cad bdug spos /
NK015(ba)026:1108: nyi zla skar gsum ni mar me /
NK015(ba)026:1109: chu bo thams cad ni dri chab /
NK015(ba)026:1110: ri bo thams cad zhal zas /
NK015(ba)026:1111: sgra grags pa thams cad ni rol mor bsgom mo //
NK015(ba)026:1113: de rnams mig gi yul du gzugs sdug /
NK015(ba)026:1117: lus kyi reg bya 'jam par bsgom mo //
NK015(ba)026:1119: snang ba thams cad mchod pa'i tshogs /
NK015(ba)026:1120: sgra grags pa thams cad rol mo dang mchod pa dbul ba'i tshig /
NK015(ba)026:1121: dran rtog thams cad de las mi 'da' bar bsgom pa'i khyer so gsum dang ma bral ba'o //
NK015(ba)026:1122: de kho na nyid kyi mchod pa ni /
NK015(ba)026:1123: 'khor 'das lam pa'i spyod pa ma lus pa rnams
NK015(ba)026:1124: bsal bzhag rdul tsam yang med pa thams cad ma
NK015(ba)026:1125: skyes pa kun tu bzang mo'i ngang du ro gcig
NK015(ba)026:1126: pas de kho na nyid dang /
NK015(ba)026:1127: de ma 'gag pa 'khor 'das lam gyis chos rnams
NK015(ba)026:1128: mchod pa'i tshogs su cir yang 'char ba ni kun
NK015(ba)026:1129: tu bzang po / de gnyis kyang ngo bo la
NK015(ba)026:1130: dbyer med pa ni gnyis su med pa byang chub
NK015(ba)026:1131: sems kyi de kho na nyid do //
NK015(ba)026:1132: drug pa phyi'i mchod pa ni /
NK015(ba)026:1133: mnyes par byed pas mchod pa /
NK015(ba)026:1134: snang grags thams cad mchoda rdzas las mi 'da' ba'i phyag rgya /
NK015(ba)026:1135: mchod pa gzhan las khyad par du gyur pas chen
NK015(ba)026:1136: po 'di ni semsa kyis cho 'phrul yida bzhina gyi
NK015(ba)026:1137: nor bu lta bu mchod sprin bsam gyi mi khyab
NK015(ba)026:1138: pa'i tshogas kyis mchod par bya ste /
NK015(ba)026:1139: de yang bdag gis thugs ka nas yi ge b+h+r+aum
NK015(ba)026:1140: phyogsa bcur spros pas sa gzhi thamsa cada la phog
NK015(ba)026:1141: pas sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams rnam par dag pa
NK015(ba)026:1142: mnyen la 'ajama pa rega na shin tu bde ba'i
NK015(ba)026:1144: 'og gzhi sna tshogas pa'i rina po che'i sa gzhi mnan na nem pa /
NK015(ba)026:1145: bteg na 'phar ba'i re'u mig mig mang ris su
NK015(ba)026:1146: mdzesa para bris shing phra mig rin po che du
NK015(ba)026:1148: t+r+aam spros pas ri thams cad la phog pas yon
NK015(ba)026:1149: tan kun 'byung ba nor bu rin chena gyis phung
NK015(ba)026:1151: a spros pas chu thams cad la phog pas dbyibsa
NK015(ba)026:1152: legas pa'i rdzing bu gsum rim dang ldan pa'i nang
NK015(ba)026:1153: du ro bro ba'i mchoga tu gyur pa'i bsila zhing
NK015(ba)026:1154: dwangs ba'i yan lag brgyad dang ldan par bsam /
NK015(ba)026:1155: b+h+r+aum spros pas khang khyim sbra gur thams cad la
NK015(ba)026:1156: phog pas rina chen gyis khang pa sna tshogsa par
NK015(ba)026:1157: bsam pa dang / t+r+aam spros pas nags tshal thams
NK015(ba)026:1158: cad la phog pas phyi snod kyi 'jig rten ni
NK015(ba)026:1160: rtsi shing thams cad dapaga bsam gyi ljon shing rgyas pa'i tshala du bsam /
NK015(ba)026:1161: t+r+aam spros pas sgra skad thams cad la phog pas
NK015(ba)026:1162: sangs rgyas byang sems rnams la bstod pa'i glu dbyangs
NK015(ba)026:1163: dang / sems can rnams la chos ston pa'i tshigas su bacada pa'i sgrar bsam /
NK015(ba)026:1164: m+aam spros pas gos rgyan dang na bun thams cad
NK015(ba)026:1165: la phog pas lhab lhub sna tshogs dang bla re
NK015(ba)026:1166: rgyal matshana lha'i na baza'a dang gdugs du bsam /
NK015(ba)026:1167: t+r+aam spros pas sems can gyi rgyan thams cad la phog pas rin po che'i do shala dang /
NK015(ba)026:1168: dpung rgyan dang se mo do ru bsam /
NK015(ba)026:1169: bam a spros pas longs spyod thams cad la phog pas /
NK015(ba)026:1170: bdud rtsi'i rang bzhin baza'a ba dang btung ba dang /
NK015(ba)026:1171: ro bro ba'i mchoga sna tshogs pa rnams dang /
NK015(ba)026:1172: h+r+aihsprosa pas skye 'gro pho mo thams cad la phog
NK015(ba)026:1173: pas 'gro ba thams cad kyang ranga la mdzesa para
NK015(ba)026:1174: brgyan pa'i mchod rdzas 'dod yon sna tshogs thogs pa'i
NK015(ba)026:1175: lha dang lha mo re res yang grangs rdul snyed
NK015(ba)026:1176: rnams kyis rkang pa'i bro dang lag pa'i gara la
NK015(ba)026:1177: sogas pa'i sgra kha nas skye ba med pa'i glu
NK015(ba)026:1178: blangs zhing bde bar gshegs pa rnams la tshigs su
NK015(ba)026:1179: bcad pa'i bstod pa bsam yasa kyis /
NK015(ba)026:1180: mang nyung gis tshad ni phyogsa bcu nama mkha'i khamas gang bar bakanga nasa /
NK015(ba)026:1181: sngar spyan drangs pa'i dkyil 'khora kun la rgyas par 'bul lo //
NK015(ba)026:1182: bdun pa phyag rgya gar tshogs kyi mchod pa la gnyis te /
NK015(ba)026:1183: dang po rang bzhin lta ba'i phyag rgya ni /
NK015(ba)026:1184: rtog tshogs thams cad sgyu 'phrula d+r+wa ba lha yab
NK015(ba)026:1185: yum 'brel bar gnas pas rang bzhin phyag rgya de
NK015(ba)026:1186: ltar mngona sum du rdzogas pa'i dus su /
NK015(ba)026:1187: dabnga po'i yul du gang gyur pa thams cada /
NK015(ba)026:1188: thabas dang shes rab dbyer med du ldan par gyur cinga /
NK015(ba)026:1189: 'khor 'das mnyam pa'i ngang nyid du rtogsa cing gasla na lta ba'i phyag rgya /
NK015(ba)026:1190: mngon du byas pa 'bras bu'i phyag rgya'o //
NK015(ba)026:1191: de gsum dang ldan pa ni thamsa cada byang chub mchog gi rgya'o //
NK015(ba)026:1192: gnyis pa ma 'gag pa rtags kyis phyag rgya'o //
NK015(ba)026:1194: dang po phyag rgya'i khungs nges tshig dang bcas pa ni /
NK015(ba)026:1195: rngam glog ltar bskyod chen ni lus kyis yan lag lnga ste /
NK015(ba)026:1196: lag pa g.yas la rdo rje rigs kyi lha brgyad /
NK015(ba)026:1197: mgo de bzhin rigs kyi lha brgyad /
NK015(ba)026:1198: lag pa g.yon rin chen rigs kyi lha brgyad /
NK015(ba)026:1199: rkang pa g.yon pad+ma rigs kyi lha brgyad /
NK015(ba)026:1200: rkang pa g.yas las kyi rigs lha brgyad kyis 'khora lo'i gzhal yas su /
NK015(ba)026:1201: thabas yab dang shesa rab yum thamsa cada kun kha dog gasla zhing 'od zer 'phro bar bsgom na /
NK015(ba)026:1202: bsgul bskyod thamsa cada phyag rgya yin pas /
NK015(ba)026:1203: 'di ni spyi rgya chena po yin te zhes so //
NK015(ba)026:1204: bla med chena po kun tu bzang posa 'di skad gsungsa /
NK015(ba)026:1205: rang bzhin gyis phyag rgya rtogs dka' bas na /
NK015(ba)026:1206: gasnga ba de nyid gzhung gang gis ston na /
NK015(ba)026:1207: de kho na nyid ngesa pa'i don mtshon par byed
NK015(ba)026:1208: pa gsang ba snying po'i gzhung gis ston pa'i phyag
NK015(ba)026:1209: rgya 'di ni 'da' bar daka'a ba ste rgyal po'i
NK015(ba)026:1211: gnyis pa lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyis phyag rgya la gnyis las /
NK015(ba)026:1212: dang po phyag rgya'i rgyu bstan pa ni /
NK015(ba)026:1213: lag pa g.yas pa mi bskyod pa'i rigs kyi sor mo bre kha lnga la /
NK015(ba)026:1214: ma sur+ya man+dala ces pas nyi ma'i dkyil 'khora lnga bkod la /
NK015(ba)026:1215: de'i steng du yab kyi sa bon yi ge lnga bkod de /
NK015(ba)026:1220: mathe'u chung la h+aa rnams so //
NK015(ba)026:1221: lag pa g.yon pa rina chen rigs kyi sor mor bre kha lnga la /
NK015(ba)026:1224: de'i steng du yum gyis yi ge 'bru lnga bkod /
NK015(ba)026:1229: mathe'u chung la t+aam rnams so //
NK015(ba)026:1230: de la lag pa g.yas g.yon gyi sor mo lnga
NK015(ba)026:1231: gnyis zung du sprad pa lasa thal mo sbyor ba'i
NK015(ba)026:1232: lha so so'i phyag rgya 'byung ba'i rgyu'o //
NK015(ba)026:1233: gnyis pa phyag rgya dngos la gnyis las /
NK015(ba)026:1234: dang po rigs lnga spyi'i phyag rgya ni /
NK015(ba)026:1235: lag pa g.yas pa'i 'dzub mo'i dang /
NK015(ba)026:1236: g.yon pa'i m+aum gnyis rtse sbyar ste /
NK015(ba)026:1237: rigs bzhi'i yi ge 'bru brgyad po yab yum brang ma sbrad par bsnol te /
NK015(ba)026:1239: dus gsum gyi rgyal ba kuna dang mnyam par sbyor
NK015(ba)026:1240: ba'i dbang dang dngos grub bde ba chena po rang
NK015(ba)026:1241: gi rgyud la sbyin par byed pa'i phyag rgya'o //
NK015(ba)026:1242: de yang ye shes rngam glog gis 'khor lo'i rgyud las /
NK015(ba)026:1243: dang m+aum gnyis rtse sbyar te //
NK015(ba)026:1244: de bzhin h'u dang l+aam gnyis sbyar /
NK015(ba)026:1246: / +aam dang p+aam yang de bzhin te //
NK015(ba)026:1247: l+aam dang t+aam gnyis sbyar ba las //
NK015(ba)026:1248: rgyab sbyar s+w+aa dang mam sbyar ba /
NK015(ba)026:1250: / 'di ni yab kyi spyi rgya yin //
NK015(ba)026:1251: lag pa thal mo sbyar ba las //
NK015(ba)026:1252: dang m+aum sbyar h'u dang ni //
NK015(ba)026:1253: l+aam sbyar s+w+aa dang p+y+aam du sbyar /
NK015(ba)026:1255: / +aam dang m+aam sbyar h+aa t+aam sgreng //
NK015(ba)026:1256: yum gyi spyi rgya yin par bshad do //
NK015(ba)026:1258: gnyis pa lha so so'i phyag rgya ni /
NK015(ba)026:1259: de la phyag rgya bzhi la don bco lnga yod kyang /
NK015(ba)026:1260: 'dir lag tu blangs pa la don tshangs dgos te /
NK015(ba)026:1263: bdag rdo rje sems dpa' la sogs rigs lnga'i lha
NK015(ba)026:1264: rnams kyi dbu'i gtsug tor nas zhabs kyis gdan khri
NK015(ba)026:1265: man chad gsal ba ni sku phyag rgya chen po
NK015(ba)026:1266: / de ltar gsal ba'i lag g.yas kyis nyi ma
NK015(ba)026:1267: la gnas pa'i yi ge 'bru bzhi po sbas nas
NK015(ba)026:1270: mathe'u chung rnams rim bzhin gyen du sgreng nas thugsa kara bakana thabs su bca' ba ni /
NK015(ba)026:1271: bca' ba dam tshig gi phyag rgya'o //
NK015(ba)026:1272: de'i rtse mora h'u mthing ka /
NK015(ba)026:1276: h+aa ljang ku rnams rim pa bsam pa ni /
NK015(ba)026:1277: bsam pa chos kyi phyag rgya'o //
NK015(ba)026:1278: de yongs su gyur pa las rdo rje rtse lnga
NK015(ba)026:1279: la sogs phyag mtshan 'od 'abra ba bsam pa ni
NK015(ba)026:1280: / bsam pa dam tshig gi phyag rgya /
NK015(ba)026:1281: lag pa g.yon pa zla ba'i dkyil 'khor lnga brtul
NK015(ba)026:1282: zhing yum gyi yig 'bru rnams sbas nas dril bu
NK015(ba)026:1283: bsila zhing skus brjid g.yas su phab ste /
NK015(ba)026:1284: yum la 'khril ba'i tshul gyi rla g.yon pa chos kyis rigs la brtena cing /
NK015(ba)026:1285: dbu g.yon du g.yo nas g.yon zur smad nas g.yon
NK015(ba)026:1286: du yum gyi zhal du blta ba'i tshul gyis phyag
NK015(ba)026:1288: bca' ba las kyi phyag rgya /
NK015(ba)026:1289: de ltar yid la bsam pa ni /
NK015(ba)026:1290: bsam pa las kyi phyag rgya yin gsungs /
NK015(ba)026:1291: man ngag ltar na 'di ni dam tshig phyag rgyar 'dod do //
NK015(ba)026:1292: h'u badz+ra d+h+rika ces sogs brjod pa /
NK015(ba)026:1293: brjod pa chos kyi phyag rgya'o //
NK015(ba)026:1294: man ngag ltar gyi las rgya ni /
NK015(ba)026:1295: phyag rgya gnas skabs drug ldan la /
NK015(ba)026:1296: dngos gzhi ma gtogs pa lnga bca' ba las kyi phyag rgya /
NK015(ba)026:1297: de'i tshe rdo rje'i ste ba'i h'u las 'od 'phros pas mdzad pa bcu gnyis mthar phyin te /
NK015(ba)026:1298: de yang 'gro ba rigs drug bsgral ba'i mdzad pa drug dang /
NK015(ba)026:1299: nyan thos dang rang rgyal 'gog pa'i mtha' las bslang ba dang /
NK015(ba)026:1300: rig 'dzin dang byang sems dag shes bya'i sgrib pa
NK015(ba)026:1301: sbyangs te mthar thug sangs rgyas kyi sar bkod pa
NK015(ba)026:1302: dang / dregs pa can thams cad dbang du bsdu ba dang /
NK015(ba)026:1303: ma mo mkha' 'gro dag gi thugs dam bskul zhing phrin las bcol ba dang /
NK015(ba)026:1304: sangs rgyas rnams la 'gro ba'i don mdzad par thugs dam bskul ba ste /
NK015(ba)026:1305: yang tshur bsdu bar bsam pa las kyi phyag rgya'o //
NK015(ba)026:1306: de'i g.yon phyogs su yum dbyings phyug ma la sogs
NK015(ba)026:1307: pa yum lnga gsal bar bsgom pa ni sku phyag
NK015(ba)026:1308: rgya chen po / lag pa g.yon pa zla ba'i
NK015(ba)026:1309: dkyil 'khor la gnas pa'i yi ge 'bru bzhi sbasa
NK015(ba)026:1310: rgya chen po / nas gung mo / 'dzub mo /
NK015(ba)026:1313: mathe'u chung rnams rim par sgreng ba /
NK015(ba)026:1314: thugsa kara bkan thabs su bca' ba ni /
NK015(ba)026:1315: bca' ba dam tshig gis phyag rgya /
NK015(ba)026:1316: de'i rtse mora m+aum mthing ka /
NK015(ba)026:1320: t+aam ljang gu rnams rim par bsam pa ni /
NK015(ba)026:1321: bsam pa chos kyi phyag rgya /
NK015(ba)026:1322: de yongs su gyur pa las dril bu bsila ba'i sgra chen po 'od 'abra bsam pa ni /
NK015(ba)026:1323: bsam pa dam tshig gi phyag rgya /
NK015(ba)026:1324: g.yas pa'i nyi ma la gnas pa'i 'bru lnga sbas nas lasa kyi rigs su brten pa'am /
NK015(ba)026:1326: yum gyi dbu yab kyi mdun nas btud de 'dzum pa'i madngas kyis sku brjid g.yon du phab /
NK015(ba)026:1327: dbu g.yas su yo ste spyan zur bstod nas yab kyis zhal du blta ba'i tshul du /
NK015(ba)026:1328: phyag rgya dngos su bca' ba ni /
NK015(ba)026:1329: bca' ba las kyis phyag rgya /
NK015(ba)026:1330: de ltar yid la bsam pa ni /
NK015(ba)026:1331: bsam pa las kyi phyag rgya /
NK015(ba)026:1332: m+aum d+ha tu shwa r+ai sogs brjod pa ni /
NK015(ba)026:1333: brjod pa chos kyi phyag rgya'o //
NK015(ba)026:1334: de la phyag rgya gnas skabs drug ldan ni /
NK015(ba)026:1341: yab g.yon du mnyam par bzhag nas g.yas su 'then nas mkha' la 'phyo zhing /
NK015(ba)026:1342: thad du g.yas su pad bskor gcig /
NK015(ba)026:1345: yang na g.yas g.yon dbus gsum la gsum gsum ste
NK015(ba)026:1346: dgu byas pa la rang rang gis sngags dang phyag
NK015(ba)026:1348: de nas phyag rgya bkrol te /
NK015(ba)026:1349: sor mo phar bstan la dpral ba'i thad du bkrol
NK015(ba)026:1350: ba'i tshul byas la ting nge 'dzin gyis mdzad pa
NK015(ba)026:1351: bcu gnyis kyi 'od zer spro ba mdzad cing /
NK015(ba)026:1352: de nas sor mo nang du bstan zhing ldog pa dang /
NK015(ba)026:1353: sa ma ya s+t+wam zhes brjod pa dang /
NK015(ba)026:1354: 'od zer bsdu ba dang dus mnyam du se gol thugs ka nas yab la g.yon dang /
NK015(ba)026:1355: yum la g.yas su bkrol bar bya'o //
NK015(ba)026:1356: sems dpa' phyin chad la rngam pa glog 'khor gyis tshig bcad ltar brjod pa yin pas /
NK015(ba)026:1357: phyag rgya re re la don drug drug dang ldan pa ste /
NK015(ba)026:1358: rang lha de dang der bsgyur ba ni phyag rgya chen po /
NK015(ba)026:1359: 'di man chad la sor mo'i rtse mor phyag mtshan dang yig 'bru bsgom pa med de /
NK015(ba)026:1360: phyag rgya'i dbyibs dang mtshan ma'i 'dzin stangs byas pa /
NK015(ba)026:1361: bca' ba dam tshig gis phyag rgya /
NK015(ba)026:1362: phyag du phyag mtshan bsnams par bsgom pa bsam pa dam tshig gis phyag rgya /
NK015(ba)026:1363: lha so so'i snying po brjod pa chos kyi phyag rgya /
NK015(ba)026:1364: gar bskor zhing phyag rgya bca' ba ni /
NK015(ba)026:1365: bca' ba las kyi phyag rgya /
NK015(ba)026:1366: phyag mtshan la mi spro ste /
NK015(ba)026:1367: rang gi thugs ka nas 'od zer spros pas sngar ltar mdzad pa bcu gnyis mdzad pa ni /
NK015(ba)026:1368: bsam pa las kyi phyag rgya'o //
NK015(ba)026:1369: rdo rje zhes pa thams cad g.yas /
NK015(ba)026:1370: rin po che zhes pa g.yon gyi brda ste /
NK015(ba)026:1371: de la lag pa g.yas kyi sor mo gsum brkyang
NK015(ba)026:1372: nas mathe'u chung bkum nas rin po che myu gu
NK015(ba)026:1373: rtse gsum ltar byas nas thugs kar bzhag ste /
NK015(ba)026:1374: g.yon pas dril bu bsil la yum la 'khyud tshul ni sa snying ngo //
NK015(ba)026:1375: g.yas g.yon gnyis khu tshur bcang nas sku'i sta zur gnyis su bzhag pa sgeg mo'o /
NK015(ba)026:1377: / 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis g.yon du smad de blta ba yab kyi dang /
NK015(ba)026:1378: yum g.yon du btud de blta ba dang /
NK015(ba)026:1379: sku'i brjid g.yon du phab pa dang /
NK015(ba)026:1380: g.yas su phab pa thams cad kun la 'gres par bya'o //
NK015(ba)026:1381: g.yas mathe'u chung mthe bong gis mnan te sor mo
NK015(ba)026:1382: gsum gshib te ral gri ltar phyar ba'am thugs kar
NK015(ba)026:1383: bzung ba dang / g.yas g.yon gnyis kyi rna ltag
NK015(ba)026:1384: tu rin po che'i phreng ba ltar bya ba ni
NK015(ba)026:1386: g.yas kyi sor mo cung zhig ma zin par bya
NK015(ba)026:1387: ste lag pa'i rgyab g.yas su lta ba snying gar
NK015(ba)026:1388: bzhag pa dang / g.yon mtheb srin gyi kha gyen
NK015(ba)026:1389: du bstan te pi wang len pa ltar byas la
NK015(ba)026:1390: bzhag pa dang / / g.yas kyi mtheb srin pi wang brdeg pa spyan ras gzigs yab yum dang /
NK015(ba)026:1391: g.yas kyi sor mo rdo rje rtse lnga pa ltar byas la /
NK015(ba)026:1392: rin chen gar thabs bskor nas thugs kar btud de /
NK015(ba)026:1393: lag pa gnyis gar byas pa'i rting la g.yon dpral bar bzung la /
NK015(ba)026:1394: g.yas yab la 'khril ba ltar byas pa phyag rdor yab yum /
NK015(ba)026:1395: g.yas kyis lag gung mo cung zhig ring bar byas te klu shing ltar thugs kar dang /
NK015(ba)026:1396: g.yon pas thugs kar thal mo gyen du bstan pa byams pa yab yum /
NK015(ba)026:1397: g.yas thugs kar po ti bzung ba ltar dang /
NK015(ba)026:1398: lag pa gnyis sna ltag tu me tog gzhong pa 'dzin pa ltar bya ba sgrib sel yab yum /
NK015(ba)026:1399: lag pa sor mo rnams snye ma'i 'bras bu g.yon pa'i thal mo sbyar nas gyen du bkan te /
NK015(ba)026:1400: gung mo mar me ltar bya ba kun bzang yab yum /
NK015(ba)026:1401: g.yas ut+pala ste sngar dang 'dra ba la lag pa'i rgyab g.yas su blta ba dang /
NK015(ba)026:1402: g.yon dung zhal gyi phyag rgya dang /
NK015(ba)026:1403: g.yas kyi mtheb srin gyis byug pa'am /
NK015(ba)026:1404: 'thor ba ltar bya ba 'jam dpal yab yum /
NK015(ba)026:1405: khu tshur bcang la thod dbyug rgya /
NK015(ba)026:1406: sor mo rdo rje gding ba'i dbyug pa rgya /
NK015(ba)026:1407: thod pa ltar sor mo zung 'jug gi ma bzung ba'i gung 'dzub bsgril ba pad+ma'i dbyug pa rgya /
NK015(ba)026:1409: gung srin gnyis bskum lhag ma bskyang pa rgya gram dbyug pa rgya'o //
NK015(ba)026:1410: khu tshur sor mo bcang ste 'dzum gnyis bkug pa dang /
NK015(ba)026:1411: de nyid 'dzub gnyis rtse sprad pa dang /
NK015(ba)026:1412: 'dzub gnyis gcig la gcig 'khyud pa dang /
NK015(ba)026:1413: de nyid bskul ba'i gar dang thal mo'i sgra'o //
NK015(ba)026:1414: sngar lta pi wang len pa /
NK015(ba)026:1417: sor mo rnams bsnol ste nang rang la bstan pa'am /
NK015(ba)026:1420: lag pa gnyis spyi bor glegs bam 'dzin /
NK015(ba)026:1422: lag pa gnyis me chu thogs pa lta so sor thab mo gyen thur du bstan /
NK015(ba)026:1425: yang na gnyis ka rdo rje'i thal mo'o //
NK015(ba)026:1426: de nas rang gtso bor gsal bar bya'o //
NK015(ba)026:1427: brgyad pa sbyor ba'i mchod pa ni /
NK015(ba)026:1428: sa ma ya ho yab kyis /
NK015(ba)026:1429: a nu r+aa ga ya ham yum gyis brjod par bsam la /
NK015(ba)026:1430: rang gi smin mtshams su sems dpa' dkar po dang yum dmar po gnyis 'khril bar bsgom /
NK015(ba)026:1431: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyi byin rlabs bsdu la bstims /
NK015(ba)026:1432: de gnyis sbyor ba mdzad pa'i 'od zer las dkyil 'khor gyi lha yab kyi grangs /
NK015(ba)026:1433: sems ma dmar mo byung bas yab rnams kyi sku la 'khril /
NK015(ba)026:1434: yum gyi grangs kyi sems dpa' dkar po byung bas
NK015(ba)026:1435: yum rnams la 'khril bas mnyes pa phul bar bsgom
NK015(ba)026:1436: la / de nas de rnams rang gi smin mtshams su bstim mo //
NK015(ba)026:1437: dgu pa sgrol ba'i mchod pa ni /
NK015(ba)026:1438: rang gi thugs ka nas ram spros pas 'gro ba
NK015(ba)026:1439: ma lus pa snod bcud dang bcas pa bsreg te
NK015(ba)026:1440: / yam spros pas thal ba ma lus par gtor nas /
NK015(ba)026:1442: rnam par shes pa h'u gi rnam pa dkar por gyur pa rnams /
NK015(ba)026:1443: bung ba mang po phyogs gcig la 'dus pa ltar byung nas /
NK015(ba)026:1444: rang gis zhal du zhugs yum gyis mkha' la phab ste /
NK015(ba)026:1445: h'u las rdo rje sems dpa'i skur gyur nas /
NK015(ba)026:1446: gtsug tu rnam par rgyal ba kun bzang gis mtshan pa /
NK015(ba)026:1447: nyi zla'i bar du bzhag nas rlung gi dal gyi steng du bzhag ste /
NK015(ba)026:1448: s+pha ra na phata kyis 'og min chos kyi dbyings
NK015(ba)026:1449: kyis pho brang du rnam snang gi mdzod sbur bstim
NK015(ba)026:1450: pa rgyas pa / yum gyi mkha' chos dbyings yum gyi b+ha gar bstim pa 'bring /
NK015(ba)026:1451: rang rdo rje sems dpa'i thugs kar bsgom pa bsdus pa dang gsum las /
NK015(ba)026:1452: 'dir bsdus pa byas kyang nyan no //
NK015(ba)026:1454: sman mtheb srin nyi zla'i skyog tu bsam nas gtor
NK015(ba)026:1455: bas lha thams cad kyi zhal du skye med chos
NK015(ba)026:1456: kyi bdud rtsi char bzhin du bab nas thim par
NK015(ba)026:1457: bsam pa'am / yang na lha mo nyi zla'i skyog
NK015(ba)026:1458: thogs pa dpag tu med pa rang gi thugs ka
NK015(ba)026:1459: nas spros pas sman de bcus nas mchod par bsam
NK015(ba)026:1460: bsam pa'am / / bcu gcig pa gtor ma'i gong
NK015(ba)026:1461: du phyi mchod rnam lnga sngags sam yid kyi 'bul
NK015(ba)026:1462: bsam pa'am / / / gtor ma'i mchod pa dngos ni /
NK015(ba)026:1469: chos kyi lha mo thugs kar thims par bsam /
NK015(ba)026:1470: bar bdud rtsi'i rgya mtsho lha tshogs rnams kyi sngags brjod cing b+ha ling+ta kh+aa ti btags pas /
NK015(ba)026:1471: bka' brgyud kyi bla ma rnams kyis ljags nyi zer lta bu dang /
NK015(ba)026:1472: yi dam lha tshogs rnams kyi ljags rdo rje'i sbu gu lta bu dang /
NK015(ba)026:1473: chos skyong rnams kyi ljags gri gug gi tshul du gsol bar bsam mo /
NK015(ba)026:1475: / 'og dug gsum sha khrag rus pa ni /
NK015(ba)026:1476: mkha' 'gro chos skyong la mchod do //
NK015(ba)026:1477: gnyis bcu pa mchod pa'i yon tan ni gzhung bzhin no //
NK015(ba)026:1478: bcu gsum pa bstod pa ni /
NK015(ba)026:1479: yang lha mo bzhi spros nas bstod par bsam mo //
NK015(ba)026:1480: de nas chos skyongs mchod bstod gzhung bzhin du byed tshar nas /
NK015(ba)026:1481: smon lam las bcol byas la /
NK015(ba)026:1482: sku gsung thugs kyi lhag chad kha bskang ba la
NK015(ba)026:1483: rim pa ltar k+aa li +aa li yig brgya rnams
NK015(ba)026:1484: 'dod la / de nas bcu gcig rdo rje'i 'gring
NK015(ba)026:1485: ra'i nang na bzhugs pa'i brgyud pa'i bla ma rnams
NK015(ba)026:1486: la gsol ba btab zer kyang /
NK015(ba)026:1487: ye shes rang snang la gang yang mi 'gal kyang /
NK015(ba)026:1488: gdul bya dang blo mtshams dgos pa'i dbang du na /
NK015(ba)026:1489: rdo rje ma tho gang bar yin pas der bzhug pa mi mtshams pa dang /
