NK015(ba)026:1490: rgyud sde mtha' dag gis 'dod pa dang /
NK015(ba)026:1491: 'di'i rgyun bshags kyi skabs su gtso bo'i dbu thog na bla ma bsgom par bshad pas /
NK015(ba)026:1492: rang gi spyi bor rtsa ba'i bla ma la brgyud
NK015(ba)026:1493: pa'i bla mas bskor bar bsam la gsol ba gdab
NK015(ba)026:1494: bo // bcu bzhi pa bsnyen pa ni /
NK015(ba)026:1495: de nas skabs 'dir gtso cher lha'i rnam pa gsal ci nus bya ste /
NK015(ba)026:1496: dang po gtso bo nas rim gyis rdzogs pa'i bar bya ba ni bsnyen pa'i rab bo //
NK015(ba)026:1497: bsnyen pa dngos la gnyis las /
NK015(ba)026:1498: dang po lha rtogs gi bsnyen pa ni /
NK015(ba)026:1499: rtog tshogs gang dang gang yin pa de /
NK015(ba)026:1500: lha gang yin par gyur nas dbu'i gtsug tor nas
NK015(ba)026:1501: 'og gi gdan khri'i bar gyi rgyan cha sngags 'khor
NK015(ba)026:1502: rnams rim par gsal bar byed pa la /
NK015(ba)026:1505: dang po ltar na gtso bo rdor sems su gsal thob nas /
NK015(ba)026:1506: rang dbus su rnam snang du bsgom la /
NK015(ba)026:1507: rdo sems ni rnam snang gi mal du bsgom la /
NK015(ba)026:1508: de bzhin du thub drug yan chad la shes par bya'o /
NK015(ba)026:1511: rang rdor sems nas lha zhe gnyis po rang rang
NK015(ba)026:1512: gi gdan thog tu shes pa go 'pho zhing bsgom
NK015(ba)026:1513: ste / gang ltar na rnam shes phung po gnas
NK015(ba)026:1514: su gyur nas rdor sems yab yum du bsgom la
NK015(ba)026:1516: rnam shes nam mkha'i ngo bo nyid //
NK015(ba)026:1517: sems phyir mtshan nyid ma skyes pa //
NK015(ba)026:1518: mi bskyod yab yum rang bzhin la //
NK015(ba)026:1519: ting 'dzin thugs su dbang bsgyur bas //
NK015(ba)026:1520: dngos grub lam rnams 'grub byed shog /
NK015(ba)026:1524: de nas rang kun bzang yab yum du bsgom la /
NK015(ba)026:1525: yid ni rang rig ma skyes sems //
NK015(ba)026:1526: kun tu bzang po'i rang bzhin las //
NK015(ba)026:1527: ting 'dzin byed por dbang bsgyur nas //
NK015(ba)026:1528: ma lus kun gyis byed por shog /
NK015(ba)026:1530: chos ni de bzhin ma skyes pa //
NK015(ba)026:1531: kun tu bzang po'i rang bzhin la //
NK015(ba)026:1532: ting 'dzin bya bar dbang bsgyur nas //
NK015(ba)026:1533: ma lus kun gyi bya bar shog /
NK015(ba)026:1534: a a a badz+r+ai b+ha dra san+ta a /
NK015(ba)026:1536: de nas rnam snang yab yum du bsgom la //
NK015(ba)026:1537: gzugs phung sa yi ngo bo nyid //
NK015(ba)026:1538: sems phyir mtshan nyid ma skyes pa //
NK015(ba)026:1539: snang mdzad yab yum rang bzhin la //
NK015(ba)026:1540: ting 'dzin sku ru dbang bsgyur bas //
NK015(ba)026:1541: dngos grub las rnams 'grub byed shog /
NK015(ba)026:1543: l+aam dee sha ra ti ces bazla'o //
NK015(ba)026:1544: tshor ba chu'i ngo bo nyid //
NK015(ba)026:1545: sems phyir mtshan nyid ma skyes pa /
NK015(ba)026:1547: / 'byung ldan yab yum rang bzhin la //
NK015(ba)026:1548: ting 'dzin yon tan dbang bsgyur bas //
NK015(ba)026:1549: dngos grub las rnams 'grub byed shog /
NK015(ba)026:1551: m+aam mo ha ra ti ces bazla'o /
NK015(ba)026:1554: sems phyir mtshan nyid ma skyes pa //
NK015(ba)026:1555: mtha' yas yab yum rang bzhin la //
NK015(ba)026:1556: ting 'dzin sems dpar dbang bsgyur nas //
NK015(ba)026:1557: dngos grub las rnams 'grub byed shog /
NK015(ba)026:1559: p+y+aam r+aa ga ra ti ces bazla'o /
NK015(ba)026:1561: / 'du byed rlung gi ngo bo nyid //
NK015(ba)026:1562: sems phyir mtshan nyid ma skyes pa //
NK015(ba)026:1563: don grub yab yum rang bzhin la //
NK015(ba)026:1564: ting 'dzin phrin las dbang bsgyur bas //
NK015(ba)026:1565: dngos grub las rnams 'grub byed shog /
NK015(ba)026:1567: t+aam badz+ra ra ti ces bazla'o //
NK015(ba)026:1568: mig gzugs sems phyir ma skyes pa //
NK015(ba)026:1569: sa snying yab yum rang bzhin las //
NK015(ba)026:1570: ting 'dzin sems dpar dbang bsgyur nas //
NK015(ba)026:1571: spyod yul yongs su dag byed shog /
NK015(ba)026:1573: h'u l+aa s+y+ae sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK015(ba)026:1575: sna dri sems phyir ma skyes pa //
NK015(ba)026:1576: nam snying yab yum rang bzhin las //
NK015(ba)026:1577: ting 'dzin sems dpar dbang bsgyur nas //
NK015(ba)026:1578: spyod yul yongs su dag byed shog /
NK015(ba)026:1580: t+r+aam m+aa l+ye sa ma ya hoces bazlo'o //
NK015(ba)026:1581: lce ro sems phyir ma skyes pa //
NK015(ba)026:1582: spyan gzigs yab yum rang bzhin las //
NK015(ba)026:1583: ting 'dzin sems dpar dbang bsgyur nas //
NK015(ba)026:1584: spyod yul yongs su dag byed shog /
NK015(ba)026:1585: h+r+aiha h'u pad+ma pa da ma /
NK015(ba)026:1586: h+r+aig+airti r+aa ga ra ham ces bazla'o //
NK015(ba)026:1587: rna sgra sems phyir ma skyes pa //
NK015(ba)026:1588: phyag rdor yab yum rang bzhin las //
NK015(ba)026:1589: ting 'dzin sems dpar dbang bsgyur nas //
NK015(ba)026:1590: spyod yul yongs su dag byed shog /
NK015(ba)026:1591: dzi ku ru p+aa na h+r+aih a n+ri ti r+aa ga y+aa mi ces bazla'o //
NK015(ba)026:1592: mig dbang 'das dus ma skyes pa //
NK015(ba)026:1593: byams pa yab yum rang bzhin las //
NK015(ba)026:1594: ting 'dzin sems dpar dbang bsgyur nas //
NK015(ba)026:1595: spyod yul yongs su dag byed shog /
NK015(ba)026:1596: mee d+ha ra ni s+w+aa h+aa /
NK015(ba)026:1597: dzad+hu pe pra be sh+aa ces bazla'o //
NK015(ba)026:1598: rna dbang da ltara ma skyes pa //
NK015(ba)026:1599: sgrib sel yab yum rang bzhin las //
NK015(ba)026:1600: ting 'dzin sems dpar dbang bsgyur nas //
NK015(ba)026:1601: spyod yul yongs su dag byed shog /
NK015(ba)026:1602: th+l+him nis+sa ram b+h+aa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK015(ba)026:1603: h'u push+pe +aa be sh+aa ces bazla'o //
NK015(ba)026:1604: sna dbang ma 'ongs ma skyes pa //
NK015(ba)026:1605: kun bzang yab yum rang bzhin las //
NK015(ba)026:1606: ting 'dzin sems dpar dbang bsgyur nas //
NK015(ba)026:1607: spyod yul yongs su dag byed shog /
NK015(ba)026:1608: h'u swa r+aa dz+aa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK015(ba)026:1609: bam d+ai ba su khi n+ai ces bazla'o //
NK015(ba)026:1610: lce dbang ma nges ma skyes sems /
NK015(ba)026:1612: / 'jam dpal yab yum rang bzhin las //
NK015(ba)026:1613: ting 'dzin sems dpar dbang bsgyur nas //
NK015(ba)026:1614: spyod yul yongs su dag byed shog /
NK015(ba)026:1615: m+aum sh+r+ai a r+aam ga ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK015(ba)026:1617: reg gi rtog pa ma skyes sems //
NK015(ba)026:1618: gshin rje yab yum rang bzhin las //
NK015(ba)026:1620: gdul bya ma lus mthar byed shog /
NK015(ba)026:1622: ma h+aa badz+ra d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai dz+wa li n+ai h'u phata /
NK015(ba)026:1624: reg yul chad pa ma skyes sems //
NK015(ba)026:1625: stobs chen yab yum rang bzhin las //
NK015(ba)026:1627: gdul bya ma lus mthar byed shog /
NK015(ba)026:1629: ma h+aa rat+na d+ha ro ma h+aa kro d+he sh+w+aa r+ai dz+wa li n+ai h'u phata /
NK015(ba)026:1631: reg dbang bdag 'dzin ma skyes sems //
NK015(ba)026:1632: rta mgrin yab yum rang bzhin las //
NK015(ba)026:1634: gdul bya ma lus mthar byed shog /
NK015(ba)026:1636: ma h+aa pad+ma d+ha ro ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai dz+wa li n+ai h'u phata /
NK015(ba)026:1638: reg pa mtshan 'dzin ma skyes sems //
NK015(ba)026:1639: bdud rtsi yab yum rang bzhin las //
NK015(ba)026:1641: gdul bya ma lus mthar byed shog /
NK015(ba)026:1643: ma h+aa karma d+ha ro ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai dz+wa l+ai n+ai h'u phata /
NK015(ba)026:1645: nga rgyal sems phyir ma skyes pa //
NK015(ba)026:1646: brgya byin dbang po'i rang bzhin las //
NK015(ba)026:1647: ting 'dzin thub par dbang bsgyur nas /
NK015(ba)026:1652: phrag dog sems phyir ma skyes pa //
NK015(ba)026:1653: thag bzang rigs kyi rang bzhin las //
NK015(ba)026:1654: ting 'dzin thub par dbang bsgyur nas /
NK015(ba)026:1660: / 'dod chags sems phyir ma skyes pa //
NK015(ba)026:1661: sh+aakya thub pa'i rang bzhin las //
NK015(ba)026:1662: ting 'dzin thub par dbang bsgyur nas /
NK015(ba)026:1665: mu ne h'u t+r+aum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK015(ba)026:1667: gti mug sems phyir ma skyes pa //
NK015(ba)026:1668: seng+ge dam brtan rang bzhin las //
NK015(ba)026:1669: ting 'dzin thub par dbang bsgyur nas /
NK015(ba)026:1674: ser sna sems phyir ma skyes pa //
NK015(ba)026:1676: ting 'dzin thub par dbang bsgyur nas /
NK015(ba)026:1681: zhe sdang sems phyir ma skyes pa //
NK015(ba)026:1682: gshin bu rje'i rang bzhin las //
NK015(ba)026:1683: ting 'dzin thub par dbang bsgyur nas /
NK015(ba)026:1688: gnyis pa mnyam rdzogs gi bsnyen pa la yang /
NK015(ba)026:1690: mnyam rdzogs chen po gnyis las /
NK015(ba)026:1691: dang po mnyam rdzogs gi tshul ni /
NK015(ba)026:1692: dkyil 'khor mi bsdu bar dang po rang nyid rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum gyi bzlas pa ni /
NK015(ba)026:1693: rang gi thugs kar sngags 'khor g.yas su 'khor nas
NK015(ba)026:1694: sngags kyi phreng ba rang gi shangs khung g.yas su
NK015(ba)026:1695: byung nas yum gyi g.yon pa brgyud de thugs kar
NK015(ba)026:1697: yang yum gyi g.yas nas rang gi g.yon du zhugs te snying kar thim /
NK015(ba)026:1698: der bsgril ma g.yas su 'khor te /
NK015(ba)026:1700: yab yum gyi sngags gnyis sbrel la bazla'o //
NK015(ba)026:1701: de nas rigs lnga nas rim bzhin du bsnyen pa de bzhin bya la /
NK015(ba)026:1702: thub drug ni rang rang gi thugs kar bskor gsung /
NK015(ba)026:1703: yang na rang gtso bo ni dbus su mi 'gyur
NK015(ba)026:1704: bar bzhugs pa la sngags brjod pas so so'i thugs
NK015(ba)026:1705: ka'i sngags la 'od zer shangs khung du byung nas
NK015(ba)026:1706: rang gi thugs kar bstim mo gsungs /
NK015(ba)026:1708: dang po rdor sems yab yum /
NK015(ba)026:1709: de nas kun bzang yab yum /
NK015(ba)026:1711: yang na dang po la kun bzang yab yum /
NK015(ba)026:1712: de nas rigs lnga la brgya rtsa re bzlas nas /
NK015(ba)026:1714: thub pa dang sgo ba la de'i phyir nyer gcig re bazla'o //
NK015(ba)026:1716: lha yab rnams bdag yab la bsdu /
NK015(ba)026:1717: yum rnams yum la bsdu la /
NK015(ba)026:1718: lha spyi'i bsnyen pa rang nyid rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum gyis bya ste /
NK015(ba)026:1724: thub pa drug rnams sbrel la bazla'o //
NK015(ba)026:1726: bsnyen pa gang ltar byas kyang bsnyen pa zin pa dang /
NK015(ba)026:1727: dngos grub kyi rten la ye shes pa spyan drangs
NK015(ba)026:1728: nas mdun gyi nam mkhar dzapa khang gcig bsgom pa'am
NK015(ba)026:1729: / yang na lha rtog gi dus su ye shes
NK015(ba)026:1730: dam tshig dbye nas dngos grub kyi rten mdun du
NK015(ba)026:1732: mnyam rdzogs dang mnyam rdzogs chen po gang gi skabs su /
NK015(ba)026:1733: bsnyen pa zin pa dang sngar bdag la bstim pa'i ye shes sems dpa' dang /
NK015(ba)026:1734: bdag dam tshig gnyis dbye la ye shes pa mdun du bsgom la /
NK015(ba)026:1735: bdag dang mdun gyi bar la 'od zer bskor bar 'dod do //
NK015(ba)026:1736: de nas dam blangs pa ni /
NK015(ba)026:1737: mdor na bsnyen pa'i dngos grub blangs ste /
NK015(ba)026:1738: thun mtshams su bab pa dang /
NK015(ba)026:1739: mdun gyi ye shes pa de nyid la /
NK015(ba)026:1740: rnam lnga kun bzang sgeg mo brgyad /
NK015(ba)026:1741: mchod pa bsdus pa tsam gyis mchod la /
NK015(ba)026:1742: de bzhina gshegas pa kun gyi badga /
NK015(ba)026:1744: dam blang pa'i tshigs bcad kyis gzhung ltar lan gcig brjod la /
NK015(ba)026:1746: phyag rgya gnas gsum du gtug pas /
NK015(ba)026:1747: dang po sangs rgyas thams cad kyi sku'i rang bzhin
NK015(ba)026:1748: can gyi 'khor lo dkar po dril bu can gyi
NK015(ba)026:1749: spyi bo'i sku rdo rje la thim par bsam /
NK015(ba)026:1751: de nas sems dpa' de nyid la bstim mo //
NK015(ba)026:1752: rjes kyi cho ga la lhag ma /
NK015(ba)026:1754: thun mtshams kyi rnal 'byor rnams te /
NK015(ba)026:1755: dang po lhag ma byed lugs gzhung du shes la /
NK015(ba)026:1756: dmigs pas kha bskang ba ni /
NK015(ba)026:1757: bdag gi thugs ka nas khro bo 'dod pa'i rgyal
NK015(ba)026:1758: mo dmar po g.yas g.yon zhags pa can phyung la
NK015(ba)026:1759: / de la sprul pa grangs med pa spros pa'o //
NK015(ba)026:1760: srog gi snying po phul ba ni /
NK015(ba)026:1761: 'og gi h'u mdzad badz+ra d+aa ka d+aa k+ai ni zhes pa sogs brjod pas phul bar dmigs /
NK015(ba)026:1762: rgyan stag sham dang g.yang ngo //
NK015(ba)026:1763: lha rnams kyi lce la h+r+aihbasama /
NK015(ba)026:1764: rang gi lce la yang h+r+aihdakara po la bdud rtsi 'phro ba'o //
NK015(ba)026:1765: rigs lnga'i 'khor du shar du brgyad /
NK015(ba)026:1766: de nas 'gres te phyogs bzhir brgyad brgyad do //
NK015(ba)026:1767: de ltar sum cu rtsa gnyis ni mo'i cha 'dzin la /
NK015(ba)026:1768: mtshams bzhi ni pho'i cha 'dzin no //
NK015(ba)026:1769: de nas phrin las bcol la /
NK015(ba)026:1770: tshar ba dang b+ha ling nang gi yi ge gsum rang la bsdu'o /
NK015(ba)026:1771: d+aa ki rnams ni rang gi bcol ba'i las myur
NK015(ba)026:1772: du bsgrub par bsam la rang rang gi gnas su
NK015(ba)026:1775: / 'di yan chad ni sngon dpal chen pos dam stsol ba'i 'khor yin la /
NK015(ba)026:1777: slob dpon pad+mas dam rtsol ba yin te /
NK015(ba)026:1778: de nyid du bsngosa na brtan mas mi thob pas gom pa bdun cu'am /
NK015(ba)026:1779: bdun la sogs pa phyir bsnur la /
NK015(ba)026:1780: de yang nam mkha' mthong sa la ma bzhag na /
NK015(ba)026:1781: nam mkha'i rgyal mo rdo rje ting lo sman gyis mi thob pas /
NK015(ba)026:1782: nam mkha' mthong sar bzhag nas sman rag bran la /
NK015(ba)026:1783: gtor ma +aahmh'u gis 'dod don du dmigs nas brtan ma bskyang /
NK015(ba)026:1785: gtor ma t+r+aam las rin po che'i mchod sdong rtse
NK015(ba)026:1786: mo gsum pa rtsa ba t+r+aam gis mtshan pa rtse
NK015(ba)026:1787: mo gsum la 'bru gsum gyi mtshan pa la /
NK015(ba)026:1788: dang po bde bar gshegs pa rnams la /
NK015(ba)026:1789: gnyis pa dam can srung ma /
NK015(ba)026:1790: gsum pas 'gro drug rnams mchod sbyin gyis khyab par bsam la bskyang /
NK015(ba)026:1791: bskyang dus su lha tshogs thams cad kyang zhal phyir gzigs par bsgom la /
NK015(ba)026:1793: de nas dz+wa la badz+ra'i sngags brjod pa tsam gyis
NK015(ba)026:1794: rang gi gnas lnga nas mtshon cha rnams spros pas
NK015(ba)026:1796: rdo rje'i rwa ba'i nang du mtshon cha'i gur drug la phog /
NK015(ba)026:1797: de la mtshon cha'i tshogs 'phros pas log par 'dren pa'i bgegs rnams bskrad /
NK015(ba)026:1798: de nas ye d+har+m+aa brjod pa tsam gyis lha tshogs rnams zhal nang du gzigs par bsam la /
NK015(ba)026:1799: mtshon cha tshur 'dus nas gur drug la thim pas sra zhing brtan par gyur par bsam /
NK015(ba)026:1800: de nas rting bshag bya ba ni /
NK015(ba)026:1801: rang gtso bo gnyis pa'i tshul du shar sgor gshegs
NK015(ba)026:1802: par bsam la lus ngag yid gsum gnang 'gyod dang
NK015(ba)026:1803: bcas te / na mo b+hud+d+ha ya /
NK015(ba)026:1806: badga ni ranga riga ye shesa blo dang ma ldan pasa //
NK015(ba)026:1807: baga med tshul gyis dam lasa 'agla gyur te //
NK015(ba)026:1808: bka'a brgyud bla ma'i thugas dang thugs rje badga ni
NK015(ba)026:1809: bag meda rdo rje semas dpa'i thugsa dang thugsa rje
NK015(ba)026:1810: badga ni ma mo mkha'a 'gro'i thugsa rjes zhes pa
NK015(ba)026:1812: de nas yi ge brgya pa 'don /
NK015(ba)026:1813: bla ma dang dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs rnams kyi
NK015(ba)026:1814: cho ga lhag chad du gyur pa'i nyes pa dag
NK015(ba)026:1815: pa'i gnang ba byin par bsam la /
NK015(ba)026:1816: rang gtso bo'i thugs kar yar la thim par bsam /
NK015(ba)026:1817: de nas lha tshogs gzhal yas dang bcas pas brjod par bsam la bkra shis brjod do //
NK015(ba)026:1818: de nas dkyil 'khor bsdu ba dang /
NK015(ba)026:1819: spyod lam gyi lha bsgom pa dang /
NK015(ba)026:1820: lus bsrung go bgo lugs ni /
NK015(ba)026:1823: rang snang dbyer med dkyil 'khor du //
NK015(ba)026:1824: thugs kyi dkyil 'khor nyid la bsdu //
NK015(ba)026:1825: h'u h'u zhes ni rab brjod pas //
NK015(ba)026:1826: chos kyis dbyings su thim par 'gyur //
NK015(ba)026:1827: de nas snying po dran tsam gyis //
NK015(ba)026:1828: phyag rgya chen po gsal gyur nas //
NK015(ba)026:1829: go bgo mtshams bcad lus bsrung ste //
NK015(ba)026:1830: de nas rnal 'byor chen po yi /
NK015(ba)026:1833: srog gi phyir yang mi gtong zhing //
NK015(ba)026:1834: spyod lam kun tu ma nyams par //
NK015(ba)026:1835: bdag nyid chen po brten par bsgom //
NK015(ba)026:1837: thog mar dkyil 'khor bsdu ba ni /
NK015(ba)026:1841: bsam yas lhun grub rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor la bsdu /
NK015(ba)026:1842: de nas rim gyis gtso 'khor rnams rigs bzhir bsdus te /
NK015(ba)026:1844: gtso bo yang ye shes sems dpa' nas /
NK015(ba)026:1847: thig le nas chos kyi dbyings su bstim mo //
NK015(ba)026:1848: gzhal yas khang brten dang bcas pa yang lha dang dus mnyam du nyi ma thal ba dang /
NK015(ba)026:1849: zer mi snang ba bzhin du bsdu'o //
NK015(ba)026:1850: yang na rim bsdus bya ste /
NK015(ba)026:1851: de bzhin gshegs pa sku'i rigs rnam snang la bsdu /
NK015(ba)026:1853: thub drug dang kun bzang yab yum gtso bo la /
NK015(ba)026:1854: rigs bzhi po yang gtso bo la bsdud nas sngar dang 'dra'o /
NK015(ba)026:1856: / 'dir las dang po pas rim sdud byas na 'thad gsung /
NK015(ba)026:1857: spyod lam gyi lha bsgom pa ni /
NK015(ba)026:1860: de las rdo rje sems dpa'i sku bsrung 'khor nas bshad pa ltar rim gyis bsgom pa'am /
NK015(ba)026:1861: yang na gcig char du rdo rje sems dpa'i skur bsgom /
NK015(ba)026:1863: sku gsung thugs byin gyis brlabs /
NK015(ba)026:1864: sems dpa' sum brtsegs dang ldan par byas nas /
NK015(ba)026:1865: badz+ra rak+sha ham zhes pas lus rdo rje'i khrab zhub lhub du g.yog par byas nas /
NK015(ba)026:1866: rkang pa'i mthe bong gnyis nas rdo rje'i rgyun thag zung re re byung nas /
NK015(ba)026:1867: rkang tshig gnyis kyi rgyab pus mo 'og /
NK015(ba)026:1869: de nas mdun rgyab tu khyer ba las /
NK015(ba)026:1871: de nas dpung mgo g.yas g.yon /
NK015(ba)026:1872: de nas sna ya re re mar la 'gro nas
NK015(ba)026:1873: lag pa'i mthe bong gnyis nas yar la lag tshig
NK015(ba)026:1874: gi nang gru tshug gi rgyab gnyis nas /
NK015(ba)026:1875: dpung mgo nas rgyun thag gnyis bsdam nas /
NK015(ba)026:1877: de nas dpral ba rnams su rdo rje rgya gram gyis mdud pa re re byas par bsgom /
NK015(ba)026:1878: rang gi 'dzub mo g.yas na h'u nag po /
NK015(ba)026:1879: g.yon na a dmar po bsam mo //
NK015(ba)026:1880: rgyun thag gis sna khrid pa ltar byas nas /
NK015(ba)026:1881: 'dzub mo g.yas la khro bo rdo rje gnod sbyin du bsam /
NK015(ba)026:1882: sku mdog nag po g.yas rdo rje /
NK015(ba)026:1883: g.yon phag rgod kyi mche ba thogs pa can 'dzub
NK015(ba)026:1884: mo g.yon la bdud rtsi thal sbyor dmar po bsam
NK015(ba)026:1885: pa las g.yas ral gri g.yon zhags pa can bskyed
NK015(ba)026:1886: la / 'dzub mo gnyis tshig mdo bcu drug tu
NK015(ba)026:1887: gtug pas khro bo zung re re ste sum cu
NK015(ba)026:1889: rgyun thag gi rtse mo smin mtshams su yod pa'i
NK015(ba)026:1890: sne mo la dar mthing ka'i cod pan yod par
NK015(ba)026:1891: bsam / 'di lus srungs go bgo 'bring po'i lugs yin no //
NK015(ba)026:1892: rgyas bsdus gnyis logs su shes so //
NK015(ba)026:1893: de nas 'dir thun bskyed lugs dang /
NK015(ba)026:1894: zhi khro mtshams sbyor thabs rnams bshad de /
NK015(ba)026:1895: dang po nang par thun mgo la mtshams bshags nas
NK015(ba)026:1896: bzung ste lha bsgom mchod bstod tshar nas nyin phyed
NK015(ba)026:1897: la ma phyin gyi bar du bsnyen pa bya /
NK015(ba)026:1898: nyin phyed la bab pa dang /
NK015(ba)026:1904: yang b+ha ling bshams nas de bzhin nyid nas bzung ste lha bsgom mchod bstod tshar nas /
NK015(ba)026:1905: nyi ma dmar thag ma chad kyi bar du bzlas pa bya /
NK015(ba)026:1907: dam blang ba'i steng la ting nge 'dzin bsnan ces pas /
NK015(ba)026:1908: mngon rtogs gsal gdab bya ste /
NK015(ba)026:1909: de nas ye shes pa bstim pa la sogs mchod bstod tshar ba dang lhag ma bya /
NK015(ba)026:1912: de nub srod nas lam nam gyis bar byed tshul de ring ltar bya'o //
NK015(ba)026:1913: de ltar nyi zhag 'phrug gcig la sngon 'gro tshar gnyis /
NK015(ba)026:1918: yang mtshams shin du dam nas rgyun du bsgom na
NK015(ba)026:1919: nyin phyed kyis lhag ma tshar nas dal mi bsdu
NK015(ba)026:1920: ba dang yang gtor ma bshams pa dang /
NK015(ba)026:1921: mngon rtogs gsal gdab nas spyan 'dren la sogs gzhung bsrang nas bzlas pa bya ste /
NK015(ba)026:1922: nyi ma thal nas dal bsdu'o //
NK015(ba)026:1923: do nub yang de ring ltar bya'o //
NK015(ba)026:1924: de nas mtshams sbyor la che 'bring chung gsum ste /
NK015(ba)026:1926: zhi ba'i dal bskyed mchod bstod tshar nas /
NK015(ba)026:1927: dkyil 'khor rim gyis bsdu ba'i stong nyid de'i thog
NK015(ba)026:1928: nas khro bo'i de bzhin nyid bsgom pa sprad nas
NK015(ba)026:1931: dbang rdzogs gsum gang rung du bsgom kyang /
NK015(ba)026:1932: las dang po bas dbang rdzogs bsgom na 'thad gsung /
NK015(ba)026:1934: zhi ba'i bzlas pa tshar nas /
NK015(ba)026:1935: lha rnams rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum la bsdu /
NK015(ba)026:1936: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyis bskul ba'am /
NK015(ba)026:1937: sngags tshar gcig brjod pas rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum /
NK015(ba)026:1938: badz+ra he ru ka yab yum du bskyed la dkyil 'khor mngon rdzogs ltar bsgom pa'o //
NK015(ba)026:1940: zhi ba'i dal ma bsdus par phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyis bskul ba'am /
NK015(ba)026:1941: yang na khro bo sum cu'i sngags brjod pas rten
NK015(ba)026:1942: gzhal yas dang brten pa lha gcig dus gcig du
NK015(ba)026:1943: bsgyur ste / rin po che'i gzhal yas ni /
NK015(ba)026:1944: dur khrod kyi gzhal yas khang du bsgyur /
NK015(ba)026:1953: kun bzang yab yum dang thub drug ni /
NK015(ba)026:1955: de nas ye shes pa'i dbang dang /
NK015(ba)026:1956: byin gyis brlabs pa'i lha lnga dang /
NK015(ba)026:1957: thugs ye shes sems dpa' gsum brtsegs rnams bsgom /
NK015(ba)026:1958: dbang phyug ma rnams khro bo rang gzhung bzhin du bsgom la /
NK015(ba)026:1959: de nas snyan gsan dbab pa nas bzung ste /
NK015(ba)026:1960: bzlas pa yan chad tshar nas /
NK015(ba)026:1961: zhi ba dang khro ba'i lhag ma ni /
NK015(ba)026:1962: phyis dus gcig byed pas chog gsungs so //
NK015(ba)026:1963: zhi ba dang phur ba la sogs khro bo gzhan dang mtshams sbyar na /
NK015(ba)026:1964: mtshams sbyor chen po ltar du bya gsungs /
NK015(ba)026:1965: dkyil 'khor nub re ltar du bsgom res byed na
NK015(ba)026:1966: yi dam lha la spangs blang mi 'gyur ba'i thabs
NK015(ba)026:1967: la / rang rang gi mchod bstod tshar nas /
NK015(ba)026:1968: bsnyen pa byed kha la sngar nub gang bsgom gyi lha spyan drangs la /
NK015(ba)026:1973: de nas do nub kyi lha gang yin gyis bzlas pa bya'o //
NK015(ba)026:1974: de ltar du mtshams sbyar na /
NK015(ba)026:1975: spangs blangs su mi 'gyur ba'i thog nas /
NK015(ba)026:1976: nus pa shin du che bar gsungs so //
NK015(ba)026:1978: las rim gsal ba'i sgron me zhes bya ba 'di /
NK015(ba)026:1979: gsang sngags rdo rje 'dzin pa ye shes rgyal mtshan
